(7562, '10x10 : fill the grid !', '10x10-fill-the-grid', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 74, '600 X 800', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/4ytoisipx15xrnfdgs9emvycv2nn0fea/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 37, 28, 0, 0, 0, 'Are you ready to play the most addictive and challenging game in the world ? 10x10 is a superb game where you need to fill a grid of 10 by 10 with puzzle blocks to form lines and destroy them ! It\'s super simple and super fun, but it really needs you to use your brain.    \n', 'Drag and drop and fill the grid with puzzle blocks to form lines and destroy them !', '10x10-fill-the-grid4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 21:08:21', '2022-07-25 21:08:21', NULL),
(6627, 'Poppy Huggy Wuggy Shooter', 'poppy-huggy-wuggy-shooter', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 82, '800 X 600', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/pqbystm4oxlg54qd34ismbldbuenvu0y/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'HotGames', 14, 6, 0, 0, 0, '\"Poppy Waggie Shooter\" is a scary action game in which you have to survive using different weapons against the onslaught of furious Huggy Waggie. In this terrifying adventure, you are trapped in Huggy Waggi\'s toy factory, where all the abandoned toys have come to life. Every night they prey on unsuspecting visitors. Walk through the colorful abandoned factory and shoot all the possessed toys that get in your way. There are a variety of weapons to choose from, so you can also have fun in this gloomy atmosphere. Be constantly aware of what surrounds you, and watch out for enemies that suddenly appear in the dark. How many days can you last in Huggy Waggie Shooter?', 'Management in the game \"Haggi Waggi Shooter\" on the computer is carried out using the mouse and keyboard arrows.', 'poppy-huggy-wuggy-shooter4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:29', '2022-07-25 20:55:29', NULL),
(6625, 'Ball Sort Color', 'ball-sort-color', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 96, '1080 X 1920', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/pxx9sk8oa2z80p7rl8o1z8v5vwbplhbe/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'puzzle game', 36, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ball Sort Color is a free leisure online game for boys that can exercise wisdom and brain. Your main task is to make each color tube have the same color ball. The game has a large number of game levels. With the deepening of the level, the difficulty is constantly improving. Come and exercise your thinking ability!', 'Mouse or tap to play.', 'ball-sort-color4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:26', '2022-07-25 20:55:26', NULL),
(6626, 'Princess Dream Bakery', 'princess-dream-bakery', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 88, '800 X 504', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/vrcd7is9fykv0s8c7762op4kltexn0wc/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'yiv.com', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Princess Dream Bakery is a lovely cooking game. Little princess loves cooking desserts since she was a little kid. One day her parents are going to travel. The little princess decides to run the cake bakery shop on her own. As her friend, come on and help her cooking delicious desserts. You will experience the cooking processes of the cakes, swiss rolls and fruit glutinous rice balls in this game. Don\'t forget to decorate the desserts with cute accessories. Enjoy!', 'Mouse or tap to play.', 'princess-dream-bakery4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:27', '2022-07-25 20:55:27', NULL),
(6624, 'Pyramid Exit : Escape Game', 'pyramid-exit-escape-game', 'HTML5', 0, 2, 20, 68, '600 X 800', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/6r7c1qonflsmu3311sc3a9gs2vygj0xx/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 37, 28, 0, 0, 0, 'Enter in unknown pyramids and to try to exit pharaonic treasures. You must find the way to move out the sarchophagus from the room by moving stone blocks. Find the right path and become the greatest pyramid thief.', 'find the way to move out the sarchophagus from the room by moving stone blocks.', 'pyramid-exit-escape-game4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:25', '2022-07-25 20:55:25', NULL),
(6623, 'Petits chevaux : small horses', 'petits-chevaux-small-horses', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 74, '600 X 800', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/l11vwvexf3t6dr2yvdjx4z9xyvheyz6b/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 38, 28, 0, 0, 0, 'You can play the game of small horses with 1, 2, 3 or 4 players. It\'s so great ! Find the board game of your childhood, with the little horses on your mobile or tablet. This great classic game, is simply one of the simplest games but also one of the best board games of all time. Play against artificial intelligence or against friends, and have as much fun as you want. Who will put all its horses in the first central box?', 'When it\'s your turn, roll the dice and move your pawns to reach the end.', 'petits-chevaux-small-horses4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:24', '2022-07-25 20:55:24', NULL),
(6621, '4GameGround - Among Us Coloring', '4gameground-among-us-coloring', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 11, 63, '960 X 540', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/fmrtcxx470f85qc8tkg24jl4elt0l5if/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', '4GameGround', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Funny astronauts from the popular game Among Us are so interesting to users around the world that they went beyond the main game and began to appear in other entertainment. A lot of puzzles and puzzles with the participation of astronauts are available today. But you can have fun coloring pictures with them.', 'Use mouse or tap the screen', '4gameground-among-us-coloring4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:22', '2022-07-25 20:55:22', NULL),
(6622, 'House Robber', 'house-robber', 'HTML5', 0, 2, 20, 98, '750 X 1334', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/2rrkw819seyf50vsi2gq03ot7silw9oi/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'puzzle game', 36, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'House Robber is a free online game with the theme of a robber for boys. In the game, you will play a robber, sneak into the house and steal all kinds of goods. Be careful to return after you get it, and don\'t be found by the security guard. Each level has its own scene, so you must be careful in stealing. The whole process is very exciting, are you confident to surpass it? Come and challenge!', 'Mouse or tap to play.', 'house-robber4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:24', '2022-07-25 20:55:24', NULL);
