(6618, 'Wedding Style And Royal Style', 'wedding-style-and-royal-style', 'HTML5', 0, 1, 10, 88, '504 X 800', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/e4e02rlkjp97uxuol73rt0mbig28rjxo/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'babygames.com', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Adella and Rebecca love royal style beautiful dresses so much that they want to change their style and try royal theme dresses. There are two styles of this theme and these girls can\'t make decisions. Could you help them to choose beautiful dress?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'wedding-style-and-royal-style4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:20', '2022-07-25 20:55:20', NULL),
(6617, 'Dragon Ninja Warriors', 'dragon-ninja-warriors', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 72, '800 X 450', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/8t5nk2f4fww3ghkm5rag3aomdsh7vdne/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Hihoy Games', 14, 31, 0, 0, 0, 'It is full of tension with Dragon Ninja Warriors and it is so fun that the battle game begins. Let\'s party!  \nThe Dragon Ninja Warriors game has a 3D appearance, rich visual effects and mysterious characters! Your enemies, who have moved from a mysterious world to your world, will surround you. Are you ready to fight? As a fearless Ninja you have to show all your skills. Use the special powers given to you. Be careful, the time counter will be activated once you use the special powers. You can\'t use that power again until the countdown is over. Remember, you have a very strong fist. You need to collect the attributes and gold that appear when you kill your enemies. You know you don\'t have eternal life when you fight. You should keep an eye on the Life Bar. You have to attack the enemy Ninjas as fast and with agile movements as you can.  \nSuspense and adventure are in this game. Click and you will be a part of this excitement!', 'Use the arrow keys to move around the game. You can follow the different special powers given to you in the lower right section of the game. Special powers are temporary. You can follow which ones you can use actively here.', 'dragon-ninja-warriors4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:19', '2022-07-25 20:55:19', NULL),
(6616, 'Zumbie Blocky Land 2022', 'zumbie-blocky-land-2022', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 91, '800 X 600', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/0b6m91r3nf5af43kjk06iea3qp2btko8/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'BestCrazyGames', 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In these fantastic zombie apocalypse games, you will have access to a wide variety of weaponry to combat a variety of zombie foes, such as those encountered in games to be played with other people. You are engaged in combat with Minecraft zombie Bots over a variety of maps at the same time. It will seem simple because you have everything you need at your disposal to battle zombies, but you will have to contend with other zombies as foes. Are you ready for zombie apocalypse games? To get some helpful hints, hiding behind things and having fun while playing these shooting games is necessary.    \nDo you like playing free online action games with other people and having access to various weapons? The only weapons you can access in the top zombie games are bullets.', 'wasd- walk     \nmouse- aim/look around/shoot', 'zumbie-blocky-land-20224.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:19', '2022-07-25 20:55:19', NULL),
(6615, 'Daddy-Housework-Little-Helper-Game', 'daddy-housework-little-helper-game', 'HTML5', 0, 2, 20, 75, '800 X 504', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/828kwgzsp5fmy8ppfa4j68nup4vnp0qa/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'JumpGame', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh, what a mess this house is! Can you take care of dad and tidy up the house before mom comes home? Do laundry, take care of puppies, clean dirty toilets, and more! Don\'t forget to leave a love note for Mom on the fridge! It\'s crazy to help clean the house, especially when mom isn\'t home!', 'Use Mouse To Play and Keyboard', 'daddy-housework-little-helper-game4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:18', '2022-07-25 20:55:18', NULL),
