(6607, 'Sniper King 2D The Dark City', 'sniper-king-2d-the-dark-city', 'HTML5', 0, 2, 15, 99, '854 X 458', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/cqns7mf36ruo0qaqbuy833f09209djpf/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'BestGameSpot.Com', 14, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Sniper King 2D The Dark City is a puzzle shooter game developed by Bestgamespot.com. Your task is eliminate enemies from a distance using your sniper rifle. Complete over 30 challenging levels with various objectives and enjoy the intuitively smooth gameplay. Your accuracy matters a great deal in this game, so does your stealth ability.', 'Aim and shoot', 'sniper-king-2d-the-dark-city4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:09', '2022-07-25 20:55:09', NULL),
