(6602, 'LAMPADA STREET GAME ONLINE', 'lampada-street-game-online', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 69, '800 X 600', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/lec6m101hnqih4c2i9qxc7thjibg1cl8/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Funis', 31, 37, 0, 0, 0, 'Lampada Street is a skill game where you are a light bulb! You have to run and jump to cross the street without being hit by cars or other lamps. You have three light bulbs for every level, and multiple checkpoints per level. If you die three times, you have to replay the level. The game has a great atmosphere, a fitting soundtrack and some nice graphics. Can you finish every level in Lampada Street?    \n   \n', 'Move - any key   \nJump - space', 'lampada-street-game-online4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:02', '2022-07-25 20:55:02', NULL),
(6601, 'Tennis Guys', 'tennis-guys', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 82, '960 X 540', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/yf97jyrdo9azrkiy72erql12lff8vy51/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'SquareLemurs', 29, 25, 0, 0, 0, 'Fun tennis physics combined with great swipe controls to give the best tennis experience on web! Keep practicing, sharpen your skills and make your way to the top in this tennis clash game.     \n', 'Swipe to shoot', 'tennis-guys4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:55:01', '2022-07-25 20:55:01', NULL),
(6599, 'Become A Florist', 'become-a-florist', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 72, '800 X 600', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/th2i1454sa0pueonhjbe99evpbxzk01u/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Playtouch', 31, 37, 0, 0, 0, 'You can now  become a florist ! Use your imagination to create the most beautiful bouquets ! Choose between tons of flower combinations, and you can even choose the color for each flower!     \n    \nHey Girls ! This game is made for you. It\'s time to create amazing bouquets.', 'Select the flowers, the decorations and the flower pot to make a beautiful bouquet.', 'become-a-florist4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:54:59', '2022-07-25 20:54:59', NULL),
(6600, 'Amazing Heroes', 'amazing-heroes', 'HTML5', 0, 1, 16, 75, '600 X 1024', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/icrahnqc9p5ihrxgdz8ghqvutx4cf3zr/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Mapi Games', 20, 28, 0, 0, 0, 'Amazing Heroes is a fun reflex game to match as many items as you can. this game is a mix of speed, memory, and skills! You want to know how your memory skill! so use the memory test in this game!  \nEnjoy!  \n  \n', 'Just one Click/Tap to play!', 'amazing-heroes4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:54:59', '2022-07-25 20:54:59', NULL),
(6598, 'Solitaire: Klondike', 'solitaire-klondike', 'HTML5', 0, 1, 20, 60, '800 X 600', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/1l3b8ub030cxazpy05snx4mqmf1juv7g/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'Armath', 31, 28, 0, 0, 0, 'The addictive game you’ve been playing on your computer for years now goes wherever you do. Whether you know it as Patience, Klondike, or just Solitaire, this popular game is one of the best games around.     \n ', 'Tap or drag cards to arrange them in descending order with alternating colors. When you can, move cards up to the foundation to sort all of the suits from Ace to King. You can draw one card at a time for a more relaxing game, or draw three for a challenge', 'solitaire-klondike4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:54:58', '2022-07-25 20:54:58', NULL),
(6597, 'Baby Taylor Crafting Fun', 'baby-taylor-crafting-fun', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 78, '504 X 800', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.co/p9xv7zllqa6jozswxhaw7dlclgrbt4ej/', 'https://gamemonetize.com', 'en', 'babygames.com', 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Taylor is a girl who likes to do crafts very much, and she often makes gifts for friends. Taylor\'s mother\'s birthday is coming up and Taylor decided to make some gifts, bags, cookies and greeting cards for her. Taylor is afraid that she will be too slow, please help her to make these gifts!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'baby-taylor-crafting-fun4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-07-25 20:54:57', '2022-07-25 20:54:57', NULL),
