(7849, 'SuperHero BMX Space Rider', 'superhero-bmx-space-rider', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 1035, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/superhero-bmx-space-rider/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Dewise Studios.', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Superhero BMX Space Rider is an awesome riding game in which you can control a variety of superheroes through some awesome intergalactic race tracks. The heroes are enjoying some down time and have decided to try out their BMX skills on their epic space track! You must help the superheroes race against the clock and complete each course as quickly as possible whilst also collecting the green spheres.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to ride\nSpace bar to push the bike forward\n', 'superhero-bmx-space-riderr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:02', '2022-08-08 16:27:02', NULL),
(7850, 'Offroad Prado Mountain Hill Climbing', 'offroad-prado-mountain-hill-climbing', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 13, 96, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/offroad-prado-mountain-hill-climbing/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Offroad Prado Mountain Hill Climbing is a superb driving game in which you can show off your off-road racing skills. The aim of this game is simple – you must attempt to drive your vehicle and reach the end destination. This might sound easy, but you are confronted with a variety of difficult and dangerous terrain that will truly test your driving skill!\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to drive\nSpace bar to use handbrake\n', 'offroad-prado-mountain-hill-climbingg.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:03', '2022-08-08 16:27:03', NULL),
(7851, 'Taxi Gone Wild', 'taxi-gone-wild', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 1115, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/taxi-gone-wild/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Taxi Gone Wild is a car racing game in which you drive as fast as possible! The challenge is to avoid hitting other cars to avoid delays to move forward onto the next level.', '\nLeft and right arrow keys = drive\nUp and down keys = control the speed\nSpace = jump\n', 'taxi-gone-wild7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:03', '2022-08-08 16:27:03', NULL),
(7852, 'Driver FRVR', 'driver-frvr', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 957, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/driver-frvr/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Driver FRVR is a driving game that lets you play as a driver trying to make a living by picking up passengers, and by sheer luck, the money scattered on the street. You\'ll also be trying to avoid other cars and obstacles to keep your vehicle in tip top shape (even a scratch on your car will lead to a game over). The money you collect is also used towards getting better cars that\'ll get you even better tips from customers. Aim to go the highest distance and get the best car available!', 'Tap and swipe/click and drag your car to the direction of the lane you\'d like to switch to.', 'driver-frvr4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:04', '2022-08-08 16:27:04', NULL),
(7853, 'Freak Taxi Simulator', 'freak-taxi-simulator', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 476, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/freak-taxi-simulator/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Freak Taxi simulator - online game for driving enthusiasts\n\nHave you ever wondered what it’s like to be a taxi driver? If you have, you can realize your dreams in this awesome taxi simulation game. This is not your standard driving game however - strap yourself in and get ready for a crazy ride through the city!\n', '\nUse the WASD keys or the arrow keys to control the car\nPress shift for Nitro\nPress space bar for the hand brake\n', 'freak-taxi-simulator2.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:04', '2022-08-08 16:27:04', NULL),
(7854, 'Cyber Cars Punk Racing', 'cyber-cars-punk-racing', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 495, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cyber-cars-punk-racing/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'performing stunts on 12 specially designed racetracks. Reaching the finish line in time', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cyber Cars Punk Racing is a 3D car driving game with futuristic cars and theme. There are super vehicles, neon city, and many game modes. 16 supercars, 60 racetracks, 2 players, 1 free ride area, Hot Pursuit area, and a battlefield are waiting for you. This game has a vehicle purchase and development system, and you can race against artificial intelligence or drive freely.', '', 'cyber-cars-punk-racing.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:05', '2022-08-08 16:27:05', NULL),
(7855, 'Racing Blast 3D', 'racing-blast-3d', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 927, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/racing-blast-3d/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Racing Blast 3D is an epic racing game with cool 3D graphics. Your aim is simple – to reach the finish line. This might sound easy, but you are racing against the clock. You are also fighting against waves of oncoming traffic that have no regard for your vehicle’s safety!\n', '\nWASD or Arrows to control the car\nSpace bar to use handbrake\nF to use nitro\n', 'racing-blast-3dd.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:05', '2022-08-08 16:27:05', NULL),
(7856, 'Trolley Racing', 'trolley-racing', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 1177, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/trolley-racing/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Tonny Nevel.', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Trolley Racing is a driving game where you should drive a shopping trolley to the finish line without falling. Be careful with the obstacles and various traps. Make sure to brake the trolley when it\'s needed. Try to complete all the levels and be the best trolley rider! Good luck!', '\nA / left arrow key = brake\nD / right arrow key = accelerate\n', 'trolley-racing.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:06', '2022-08-08 16:27:06', NULL),
(7857, 'Offroad Racing', 'offroad-racing', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 339, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/offroad-racing/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Sandy.', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Offroad Racing is the ultimate off-road driving game in which you will race a giant a host of other players. You will be able to race through some of the most beautiful locations ranging from snowy mountains to the barren desert. Jump behind the wheel and prove your driving skills.\n', '\nArrow keys to drive\nC to change the camera to another car\nV to change current car\'s view\nAZ to shift gear\n', 'offroad-racingg.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:06', '2022-08-08 16:27:06', NULL),
(7858, 'Micro Pilots', 'micro-pilots', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 79, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/micro-pilots/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Martijn Kunst.', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Micro Pilots is a fun 2D arcade game in which you must pilot small aircrafts orbiting around a selection of beautiful planets. You must successfully fly around the planet without colliding with anything on the planet or even the planet itself. Each orbit will become harder and harder as you gain speed and more obstacles become apparent.\n', '\nTo steer right, press right arrow, X or left mouse button\nTo brake, press left arrow, Z or right mouse button\nSpace bar to throw a bomb\n', 'micro-pilots8.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:07', '2022-08-08 16:27:07', NULL),
(7859, 'Decorate My BMW M5', 'decorate-my-bmw-m5', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 18, 243, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pimp-my-bmw-m5/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Decorate the BMW to look as cool and pimped out as possible.', 'Drag the left mouse button to move the parts.', 'decorate-my-bmw-m50.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:08', '2022-08-08 16:27:08', NULL),
(7860, 'Moto Maniac', 'moto-maniac', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 918, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/moto-maniac/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'IriySoft.', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Just like Moto X3M, Moto Maniac lets you drive a dirt bike and overcome challenging obstacles-filled courses to safely reach the finish line.\n', '\nW or up arrow to accelerate\nS or down arrow to move backward\nA/D or left/right arrow to tilt the bike\n', 'moto-maniac9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:09', '2022-08-08 16:27:09', NULL),
(7862, 'Micro Racers 2', 'micro-racers-2', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 18, 205, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/micro-racers-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Micro Racers 2 was', 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Micro Racers 2 is a racing game where you choose your favorite car and track to race with the others. Try to win first place.', '\nUp arrow key = accelerate\nDown key = brake\nLeft arrow key = steer left \nRight arrow key = steer right\nSpace = nitro boost\n', 'micro-racers-20.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:27:10', '2022-08-08 16:27:10', NULL),
