(8021, 'Hobo 3', 'hobo-3', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 1013, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hobo-3/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hobo 3 is a fantastic fighting game that you can play on CrazyGames.com directly in your browser. You will find this game unblocked. The game is built with HTML5 technology to work in all modern browsers. If you enjoy playing Hobo 3, also play our other fighting games or Clash of Skulls and Bandit RIP.', '', 'hobo-33.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:24', '2022-08-08 16:28:24', NULL),
(8022, 'Territory War', 'territory-war', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 1164, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/territory-war/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Territory War is a fun and exciting turn-based strategy game in which you control a squad of stickmen soldiers. You can play in three different game modes - campaign, challenges and custom battle. Before you start fighting, you can choose the name of each of your team members and your team name!\n', '\nLeft and right arrow to move\nSpace bar to jump\n1234 to use action\n', 'territory-war6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:24', '2022-08-08 16:28:24', NULL),
(8023, 'Samurai Madness', 'samurai-madness', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 795, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/samurai-madness/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Samurai Madness is', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Samurai Madness is an action game that is a mix of roguelite, action, and casual play styles. Lead the fierce samurai warrior on his way to take vengeance on the evil syndicate! Prove your dexterity in this action game full of challenging encounters. Be smart, fast, and agile. Make wise and swift decisions.', 'Drag the left mouse button to draw the move and attack path.', 'samurai-madness.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:25', '2022-08-08 16:28:25', NULL),
(8024, 'Hello Guys', 'hello-guys', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 826, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hello-guys/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hello Guys is a side-scrolling arcade game that combines running and platforming. Run, race, slide, jump, fall, flip, slam, and break crazy obstacles with other opponents. These hurdles become more challenging, ridiculous, and super fun as you move forward.\n', '\nAD or left and right arrows to move\nW or up arrow to jump\n', 'hello-guys.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:25', '2022-08-08 16:28:25', NULL),
(8025, 'Wacky Dungeon', 'wacky-dungeon', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 984, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/wacky-dungeon/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wacky Dungeon is a cartoonish action-packed RPG in which you can fight interactive battles against the weirdest of enemies.\n', '\nLeft mouse button on PC \nTapping the touch screen of mobile devices\n', 'wacky-dungeon.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:26', '2022-08-08 16:28:26', NULL),
(8027, 'Wholesome Cats', 'wholesome-cats', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 747, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/wholesome-cats/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wholesome Cats is an adventure game based on the world of cats in which you must travel around the beautiful island seeking new friends and challenges for your cat gang. If you love cats then you are in the right place, this cat world contains cats everywhere you look. There are more than 50 species of cats for you to find and befriend. ', 'Use the left mouse button to do an action.', 'wholesome-catss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:27', '2022-08-08 16:28:27', NULL),
(8029, 'Spider Hero Street Fight', 'spider-hero-street-fight', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 298, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/spider-hero-street-fight/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Spider Hero Street Fight is an epic platform game featuring everyone\'s favourite superhero Spiderman! Spiderman is patrolling the streets as usual and trying to keep the civilians safe but there are plenty of bad guys on the loose and he must do whatever he can to stop them!\n', '\nArrow keys to move\nZ to punch\nX to kick\nC to block\nSpace bar to jump\n', 'spider-hero-street-fightt.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:28', '2022-08-08 16:28:28', NULL),
(8030, 'Tank Battle: War Commander', 'tank-battle-war-commander', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 146, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tank-battle-war-commander/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Playtouch.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tank Battle: War Commander is an epic turn based strategy game in which you must choose to fight for either the Axis or Allied powers during World War 2. Whichever side you choose, you must fight to repel the enemy invasion and eradicate their forces. During each turn, you must choose which course of action to take – you can choose between three different actions. Once you have chosen, a slot machine will randomly decide how effective your actions were.\n', '', 'tank-battle-war-commanderr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:28', '2022-08-08 16:28:28', NULL),
(8031, 'Grand Action Simulator: New York Car Gang', 'grand-action-simulator-new-york-car-gang', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 361, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/grand-action-simulator-new-york-car-gang/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'HGames.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Grand Action Simulator: New York Car Gang is an awesome open world crime game with similarities to the popular GTA series. You must take the role of a ruthless criminal with city-wide aspirations – he wants to rule a crime empire and take over NYC using any means necessary. Explore the cityscape and collect money using whatever methods you feel are appropriate.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys: move\nT: open nearby garage\nLeft click: shoot or punch\nSpace bar: jump\nLeft shift: run\nX: switch weapon\nF: open car\nR: open nearby shop\nG: grenade\nZ: switch grenade\nC: switch vehicle camera\n', 'grand-action-simulator-new-york-car-gangg.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:29', '2022-08-08 16:28:29', NULL),
(8032, 'Duck Life: Space', 'duck-life-space', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 1176, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/duck-life-space/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'purchasing them in the shop, creating an elite fleet of avid avian racers. As well as new ducks, you', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Duck Life: Space is a duck racing game with a galactic story and theme. An alien from outer space has nabbed your trophy, and you need to go on a quest through space to get it back! Enjoy a plethora of new mini-games and races along the way.\n', '', 'duck-life-spacee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:29', '2022-08-08 16:28:29', NULL),
(8033, 'Duck Life 4', 'duck-life-4', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 1101, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ducklife-4/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'training your duck’s core skills. These skills are running, flying, climbing, and swimming. You have', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Duck Life 4 is a duck racing game set after the ban on genetically modified ducks. A year has passed since the ban on genetically modified ducks and now it’s up to you to defeat the world champion. Train your duck team to compete in six new locations around the world.', '', 'duck-life-4b.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:30', '2022-08-08 16:28:30', NULL),
(8034, 'Duck Life', 'duck-life', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 795, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ducklife/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'playing various minigames that increase your running, swimming, and flying abilities. The duck will ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Duck Life is the first game in the Duck Life series. A tornado has struck your farm and destroyed everything. All that remains is a single duck egg. Train this duckling to peak athletic form so you can earn money to rebuild the farm.', '', 'duck-lifee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:30', '2022-08-08 16:28:30', NULL),
(8035, 'Kung Fu Grandpa', 'kung-fu-grandpa', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 124, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kung-fu-grandpa/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kung Fu Grandpa is a side-scrolling beat-em-up game where you play as a grandpa who\'s just tired of the fighting going on outside his home, and is now taking matters into his own hands. Punch and kick everything and everyone in your way as you try to bring peace back to your neighborhood. Pickup money you can use to upgrade your fighting skills, as well as weapons you can use to further beat up anything that walks into your general direction. You may be old, but that doesn\'t mean you don\'t pack a mean punch behind your fists!', '\nArrow keys = move\nZ = punch\nX = kick\nC = special power\nSpace = jump\n', 'kung-fu-grandpa7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:31', '2022-08-08 16:28:31', NULL),
(8036, 'Stickman Destruction 3 Heroes', 'stickman-destruction-3-heroes', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 16, 114, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stickman-destruction-3-heroes/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Stickman Destruction 3 Heroes is', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stickman Destruction 3 Heroes is a ragdoll physics action game. Crash the stickman into obstacles, send him tumbling down staircases and through walls into oblivious bystanders. Cause as much destruction as possible to earn the most gold!', '', 'stickman-destruction-3-heroes.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:31', '2022-08-08 16:28:31', NULL),
(8037, 'Cute Army: A Cat Story', 'cute-army-a-cat-story', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 512, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cute-army-a-cat-story/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'CuteArmy.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cute Army: A Cat Story is a stealth game in which you play as Kim who has a mission to save the Cuties around the house.\n', '\nMove: WASD or arrow keys\nDash: left shift (once unlocked)\nSmoke bomb: Q or X (once unlocked)\nPause: P\n', 'cute-army-a-cat-story.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:32', '2022-08-08 16:28:32', NULL),
(8038, 'Clash of Tanks', 'clash-of-tanks', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 518, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/clash-of-tanks/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Clash of Tanks was', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Get ready for battle in this awesome RTS tank game. In Clash of Tanks, you become the army commander. You must deploy your tank carefully and think about where the enemy tanks are placed - don\'t get caught out or out-maneuvered.', 'Drag the left mouse button to deploy a tank.', 'clash-of-tanks1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:32', '2022-08-08 16:28:32', NULL),
(8039, 'Bowmaster Prelude', 'bowmaster-prelude', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 379, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bowmaster-prelude/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bowmaster Prelude is one of the original browser games and was released over 10 years ago! This title is still as awesome as it was back then and the gameplay is addictive and fun. You must defend your castle from waves of incoming enemies and also try to attack the enemy castle. You control a brave Bowmaster and you must manually fire arrows at the incoming knights and warriors. Take into consideration the angle and power of your bow shots and also the movement of the enemies.\n', '', 'bowmaster-preludee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:33', '2022-08-08 16:28:33', NULL),
(8040, 'Robot City Simulator', 'robot-city-simulator', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 1092, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/robot-city-simulator/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'destroying buildings and objects. The points you earn can be used to purchase upgrades and new parts', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Robot City Simulator is an awesome game of rampage and mayhem in which you must control a variety of gigantic and bloodthirsty robots and attempt to smash several different cities to oblivion! If you like this type of game, you will love Crazy Pig Simulator too.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nLeft click or ctrl to attack\nSpace bar to jump or fly with the jetpack\nF to fire bazooka\n', 'robot-city-simulatorr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:33', '2022-08-08 16:28:33', NULL),
(8041, 'Google Maps Tower Defense', 'google-maps-tower-defense', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 969, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/google-maps-tower-defense/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Select a location, place towers, and battle attacking waves. Have fun with Google Maps Tower Defense! This game is made by Duncan Barclay.', '', 'google-maps-tower-defensee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:34', '2022-08-08 16:28:34', NULL),
(8042, 'Tri-Achnid', 'tri-achnid', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 490, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tri-achnid/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Tri-Achnid was', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tri-Achnid is an action game about guiding a three-legged creature who wants to save its egg sack and larvae after its mate has been eaten by a large monster.', '\nWASD = position its head to balance its body\nDrag the left mouse button on the feet = move\n', 'tri-achnid3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:34', '2022-08-08 16:28:34', NULL),
(8045, 'Battle Masters', 'battle-masters', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 1120, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/battle-masters/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Battle Masters is a fighting game that lets you duke it out with 3 other fighters in awesome one-on-one matches to the death! The game plays in a rock-paper-scissors format - each turn, both of you will choose a hand, and the winner gets a chance to select an action from a list of commands. The winner can choose to either attack, use a skill, use an item, or wait. You\'ll keep doing this until either one has lost all of their HP. Choose your fighter and may luck be on your side!', 'Click on the hands on the left side of the screen to choose a hand to throw. You\'ll also click on the context menus to choose an option to use.', 'battle-masters4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:39', '2022-08-08 16:28:39', NULL),
(8046, 'Whack Your PC', 'whack-your-pc', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 13, 280, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/whack-your-pc/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Whack Your PC is another episode of the Whack Your series. This time, you need to find several ways to destroy your computer!\n', '', 'whack-your-pc0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:39', '2022-08-08 16:28:39', NULL),
(8049, 'Rio Rex', 'rio-rex', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 1054, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/rio-rex/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Rio Rex was', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rio Rex - cause destruction in Brazil! This time you are let loose in the beautiful Rio de Janeiro but take a look back at the previous cities that have been destroyed in Mexico Rex and LA Rex.', '\nAD or left/right arrow to move the T-Rex\nW or up arrow to jump\nLeft click to chew\nHold left click to shoot fire breath\n', 'rio-rex8.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:41', '2022-08-08 16:28:41', NULL),
(8050, 'Emerald and Amber', 'emerald-and-amber', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 1066, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/emerald-and-amber/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'NoaDev.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Help Emerald to get to Amber. Get stuck to the platforms to reach the goal!\n', '\nA /D or arrow keys = move\nH/W/up arrow or space bar = jump\n', 'emerald-and-amber.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:41', '2022-08-08 16:28:41', NULL),
(8051, 'Miami Shark', 'miami-shark', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 343, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/miami-shark/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Miami Shark is an intense action game in which you control a shark that needs to cause havoc in the Miami water.\n', '\nArrow keys = move\nCtrl or A = bite\n', 'miami-shark3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:42', '2022-08-08 16:28:42', NULL),
(8052, 'Armed With Wings 3', 'armed-with-wings-3', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 113, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/armed-with-wings-3/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Super Sun Studios.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Armed With Wings 3 is the third episode of the Armed With Wings series, a full action side-scrolling platformer game.\n', '\nArrow keys to move\nW to switch between eagle/character\nA to do a melee attack\nS to swing the sword\n', 'armed-with-wings-33.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:42', '2022-08-08 16:28:42', NULL),
(8053, 'Shorties\' Kingdom 3', 'shorties-kingdom-3', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 638, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/shorties-kingdom-3/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Denis Vasilev.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Our heroes are back for more adventure. Help the three legendary heroes to slay enemies across the continent.', '', 'shorties-kingdom-37.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:43', '2022-08-08 16:28:43', NULL),
(8054, 'Mastermind: World Conqueror', 'mastermind-world-conqueror', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 800, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mastermind-world-conqueror/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'The-Swain', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mastermind: World Conqueror is a tactical game where you manage your troops, defend your base, and conquer the world!', '\nLeft-click = interact\nSpace = lock camera view\n', 'mastermind-world-conqueror9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:43', '2022-08-08 16:28:43', NULL),
(8055, 'Feudalism', 'feudalism', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 673, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/feudalism/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Vitaly Zaborov', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Feudalism is an open world battle game in which you need to manage your soldiers and expand your power.', 'Keyboard and mouse', 'feudalism3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:43', '2022-08-08 16:28:43', NULL),
(8056, 'Chaos Faction', 'chaos-faction', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 1096, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/chaos-faction/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'EON.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Chaos Faction is an intense arena fighting game.\n', '\nSpace Bar = Pause/Menu\nLeft and right arrow keys = move\nUp arrow key = jump\nDown arrow key = shield\nZ and X = attack\n', 'chaos-faction1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:44', '2022-08-08 16:28:44', NULL),
(8057, 'Duck Life 2', 'duck-life-2', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 280, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ducklife-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'training your duck’s core skills; running, flying, climbing, and swimming. If you enter a race befor', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Duck Life 2 is a duck racing game with various training levels to improve your athletic abilities. When you’ve trained enough, you enter a duck ‘quadrathlon’’ that puts your running, climbing, swimming, and flying skills to the test. Just another day in the life of a duck!\n', '', 'duck-life-22.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:45', '2022-08-08 16:28:45', NULL),
(8058, 'Rogue Tower', 'rogue-tower', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 842, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/rogue-tower/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rogue Tower is an action game to conquer the tower by defeating all the monsters on 100 floors. Earn gold and gem by defeating the monsters and use them to level up your character and also upgrade the potions.', '\nLeft-click = Interact with the menus or use skills \nQ = use skill 1\nW = use skill 2\nE = use skill 3\nR = use skill 4\nD = use health potion\nF = use stamina potion\n', 'rogue-tower.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:28:45', '2022-08-08 16:28:45', NULL),
