(8142, 'Idle Breakout', 'idle-breakout', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 710, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/idle-breakout/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Kodiqi.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Idle Breakout Game modernizes the Atari classic Game. Classic breakout for the Atari was a superb game. This modern idle game, however, takes the genre to the next level. During the game, you have to click the colored blocks to earn cash. Each block you click earns you a set fee - this can be upgraded. You can then use the cash to purchase breakout balls and upgrades so that you can smash the blocks faster.\n', '', 'idle-breakout8.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:29:27', '2022-08-08 16:29:27', NULL),
