(8147, 'Heroic Battle', 'heroic-battle', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 204, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/heroic-battle/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Nerdy Orc Studio and published here on CrazyGames.com.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Heroic Battle is not like any other browser game - this fantastic game combines elements of an idle game together with strategy and RTS features. You control a castle and it is up to you to build and train an army to defeat the hordes of monsters that try to destroy you. You can build a footsoldier, and archer, a mage and a celest - each troop has a weapon that can be upgraded. You can also increase your troops health so they can take more damage.\n', '', 'heroic-battlee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:29:30', '2022-08-08 16:29:30', NULL),
