(8304, 'Tower Merge', 'tower-merge', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 443, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tower-merge/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tower Merge is a game about merging blocks and increasing income. You start with one tower but are then able to get more towers. Special towers give you special bonuses. Try to make the tallest tower and reach the highest numbers. ', 'Left-click to buy the upgrades', 'tower-merge.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:30:59', '2022-08-08 16:30:59', NULL),
(8305, 'Vaccine Idle', 'vaccine-idle', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 936, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/vaccine-idle/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Vaccine Idle is a mouse-only idle game to make your own vaccine and save the world from the virus. After each win, you can upgrade your vaccine and make it better! Save the world as soon as you can. Buy doctors and sellers, get money, and don\'t kill too many people.\n', 'Left mouse button', 'vaccine-idle.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:00', '2022-08-08 16:31:00', NULL),
(8306, 'Matches', 'matches', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 15, 370, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/matches/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Matches is a clicker game where you collect matches and destroy various objects! Start by clicking your matchbox and work your way towards various upgrades like turrets and new items. There are also achievements and a prestige system in the game.', 'Left-mouse button to interact', 'matches.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:01', '2022-08-08 16:31:01', NULL),
(8307, 'IdleByte 2', 'idlebyte-2', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 226, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/idlebyte-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'IdleByte 2 is the second installment of the fun IdleByte series. In this second game, you are waging a war of file destruction and data shooting. You are fighting for the good side and must use your files to destroy the enemies data!\n', '\nQ or W to rotate\nLeft click to buy\n', 'idlebyte-21.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:01', '2022-08-08 16:31:01', NULL),
(8308, 'Slime Farm 2: Gold Rush', 'slime-farm-2-gold-rush', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 1044, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/slime-farm-2-gold-rush/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Vad Games, the same developer of My Sugar Factory, a game in which are in charge to run a sugar fact', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Slime Farm 2 Gold Rush is an idle-farming game to create your own slime farm! Feed them, buy new ones, and improve old ones. You can also customize the color of the slime. Breed slimes, get some money, and become the richest. And also for those who like to challenge themselves, there are several achievements in the game!\n', '', 'slime-farm-2-gold-rush.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:02', '2022-08-08 16:31:02', NULL),
(8309, 'Lunar Atoms Tycoon', 'lunar-atoms-tycoon', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 16, 728, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/lunar-atoms-tycoon/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Lunar Atoms Tycoon is an incremental game that takes place in the distant future where people on the Moon discovered a new kind of atoms capable of producing plasma clots. The game\'s goal is to develop your industry to produce and process the plasma into nano fuel.\n', '', 'lunar-atoms-tycoon.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:03', '2022-08-08 16:31:03', NULL),
(8310, 'Glass Factory 2', 'glass-factory-2', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 13, 443, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/glass-factory-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Glass Factory 2 is a clicker game in which you can earn money by mining and selling sand. Buy new mining tools and upgrade them to unlock workers. By opening a factory, you can melt sand into glasses and sell them. Having saved enough money, you can purchase additional equipment for glass processing. ', 'Left mouse button', 'glass-factory-2.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:03', '2022-08-08 16:31:03', NULL),
(8311, 'Mining for the Village', 'mining-for-the-village', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 540, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mining-for-the-village/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Vad Games.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mining for the Village is a clicker game where you need to gather some resources, make some money, buy tools, build, and improve facilities for the maintenance of residents. Build your settlement from scratch.', 'Use the left mouse button to play this game', 'mining-for-the-village.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:04', '2022-08-08 16:31:04', NULL),
(8312, 'Mining in Notebook 2', 'mining-in-notebook-2', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 123, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mining-in-notebook-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Vad Games.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mining in Notebook 2 (Colony) is the second part of the idle-clicker in a notebook style. Now you have to develop your village and extract resources. Also, the concept of buying many different instruments has been preserved.\n', '', 'mining-in-notebook-2.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:04', '2022-08-08 16:31:04', NULL),
(8313, 'Cat Clicker RE', 'cat-clicker-re', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 932, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cat-clicker-re/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Cat Clicker RE is the remastered edition of the first Cat Clicker game, which now comes with different gameplay. Each upgrade produces the upgrade over! Upgrade your cat, make him look cooler by sacrificing. Buy cursors, mice, cheese to get more cat points, and reach the highest number. Have fun in this cat-clicking game.', 'Left mouse button', 'cat-clicker-re.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:04', '2022-08-08 16:31:04', NULL),
(8314, 'Mining Rush', 'mining-rush', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 691, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mining-rush/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mining Rush is a clicker game where you can mine minerals, earn money, and buy new mining tools. Not just like an ordinary clicker game, this time you can also get construction materials and build your own city. The game has 60 different tools that you can unlock! Have some fun mining!', 'Use the left mouse button to click on the rock.', 'mining-rush.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:05', '2022-08-08 16:31:05', NULL),
(8315, 'Slime Farm Remake', 'slime-farm-remake', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 241, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/slime-farm-remake/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Slime Farm Remake is', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Slime Farm Remake is a clicker game in which you have to breed slimes that bring you money. There are eight types of different slimes that you can breed. You can also dress them up in different hats to make them look fancy, buy flowers for them, build a monument or even put up a music center. There are also exciting events waiting for you during the game.', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with the buttons.', 'slime-farm-remake.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:06', '2022-08-08 16:31:06', NULL),
(8316, 'Multiplier Grid', 'multiplier-grid', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 234, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/multiplier-grid/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Multiplier Grid is a simple idle game in which you have a grid of cells, and each cell gives a multiplier to the total income. You can upgrade your cell from 2x2 to 10x10. Have fun and reach infinity many times!\n', '\nClick cells. Click cell 2 times to flush all points (also can set 1 click of hover)\nU - to upgrade speed\nM - max speed upgrade\nA - ascend\nG - grade up\nD - degrade\n', 'multiplier-grid.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:06', '2022-08-08 16:31:06', NULL),
(8317, 'Alchemical Roots', 'alchemical-roots', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 1011, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/alchemical-roots/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Alchemical Roots is a clicker game about alchemy in which you collect alchemical ingredients and use them to buy upgrades, as well as to build your own alchemist village. There are 48 different ingredients, 24 achievements, various improvements, and perks that you can unlock as you progress throughout the game.', 'Left-click to play', 'alchemical-roots.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:07', '2022-08-08 16:31:07', NULL),
(8318, 'Idlebyte RE', 'idlebyte-re', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 18, 72, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/idlebyte-re/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Idlebyte RE is a clicker-idle game about managing computer memory.\n\nThis is a remake of the original good IdleByte Flash game from 2015. The new version has enchanted graphics, better balance, bugfixes, and mobile support. Feel happy to play an old good game and have fun! You manage computer memory, buy different upgrades, get more memory, and exp. You can also level up, and you can spend your stat points for upgrading your stats.\n\nEvery 50 buildings increase the building level. When you have many YottaBytes of memory, you can gain chips from your memory. Each chip increases your memory income by 25%. Also, you can buy upgrades on your chips. The goal of this game is to buy the mystical upgrade.\n', 'Click the screen or press \"C\" to speed up the tick bar.', 'idlebyte-re.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:08', '2022-08-08 16:31:08', NULL),
(8319, 'Mining In Notebook 3', 'mining-in-notebook-3', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 434, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mining-in-notebook-3/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Vad Games', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mining In Notebook 3 is a new part of the clicker game for mining resources in a notebook. There are 40 different mining tools in the game. Try to open them all!', 'Mouse only or screen tap', 'mining-in-notebook-3.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:08', '2022-08-08 16:31:08', NULL),
(8320, 'Civilization Clicker', 'civilization-clicker', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 15, 605, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/civilization-clicker/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Civilization Clicker is a smashing clicker game. You can check it out on this page directly in your browser. It is available as an unblocked game. This highly addicting clicker game uses HTML5 to work without trouble in all modern browsers. The game contains controls to get you started. That way, it is easy to see how to play the game. If you enjoy the game, also play our other clicker games or Planet Clicker 2 and Candy Clicker 2.', '', 'civilization-clickerr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:09', '2022-08-08 16:31:09', NULL),
(8321, 'Snowflakes Idle RE', 'snowflakes-idle-re', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 905, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/snowflakes-idle-re/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Snowflakes Idle RE is a remastered HTML5 edition of Idle Snowflakes. This game is about snowflakes with a multipliers game system. Collect snowflakes or wait till they fall. There are 15 colors of snowflakes and ten forms; collect as much as possible and make snowflakes bigger and bigger. Prestige and get more and more snowflakes. Have fun with them. Make this winter great!', 'Collect snowflakes using your mouse. Left-click to buy upgrades and prestige.', 'snowflakes-idle-re.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:10', '2022-08-08 16:31:10', NULL),
(8322, 'Simple Loot Idle', 'simple-loot-idle', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 83, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/simple-loot-idle/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Simple Loot Idle is a clicker game to equip your hero with the better loot items you get from killing monsters. Sell loot which is worse and get some money to upgrade your hero. Become the strongest warrior in the world!', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with in-game buttons.', 'simple-loot-idle.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:11', '2022-08-08 16:31:11', NULL),
(8323, 'Moth Idle', 'moth-idle', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 868, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/moth-idle/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Moth Idle is a simple idle game where you have a field of lamps and some moths. The moths like light and absorb it, and each absorption makes them stronger. ', 'Use the left mouse button to buy the upgrades.', 'moth-idle.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:11', '2022-08-08 16:31:11', NULL),
(8324, 'Idle Arkanoid', 'idle-arkanoid', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 156, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/idle-arkanoid/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Idle Arkanoid is an idle game that is inspired by the legendary and familiar game to all of us from childhood - Arkanoid. Now with the beloved incremental mechanics. Watch how the blocks are destroyed and buy new improvements in the store.', 'Left mouse button', 'idle-arkanoid.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:12', '2022-08-08 16:31:12', NULL),
(8325, 'Nu Life', 'nu-life', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 744, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/nu-life/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'denisolenison.', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nu Life is an idle game about little and cute noses. Yes, Nus are cute nose-like alien creatures from planet Nu-2000. They like it when it\'s cold, and they become smaller. So, use your cold turrets and shot the Nus to make them smaller and happier! Have fun with these Nus and 10 different turrets. There is also a prestige system and there will be more updates in the future!', '\nLeft mouse button to interact\nSpace bar to spawn a Nu\nLeft arrow key to decrease the level\nRight arrow key to increase the level\n', 'nu-life.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:13', '2022-08-08 16:31:13', NULL),
(8326, 'Idle Miner', 'idle-miner', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 18, 1044, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/idle-miner/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Idle Miner is', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Idle Miner is an idle game about a cat who loves mining and getting different resources. There are 25 different resources; you can sell them or use them for crafting better pickaxes. Craft better and better pickaxes and mine into the depths of Earth. Also, there are 9 upgrades that will help you get better materials and craft better pickaxes. After level 50 you can prestige to make your cat stronger!', 'Left-click to buy upgrades.', 'idle-miner.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:13', '2022-08-08 16:31:13', NULL),
(8327, 'Apple Tree Idle', 'apple-tree-idle', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 154, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/apple-tree-idle/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Apple Tree Idle is', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Apple Tree Idle is a clicker-idle game about cats who like apples so much! Manage them, help them collect apples from the tree, and sell the apples for profit. Also you can make magical apples, eat them, and increase your income. What about apple juice? Yes, you can make it too! Manage your cats and try to make it as fast as it possible!', 'Left mouse button', 'apple-tree-idle.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:14', '2022-08-08 16:31:14', NULL),
(8328, 'Enc0de', 'enc0de', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 991, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/enc0de/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Enc0de is', 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Enc0de is an idle clicker game to improve the game\'s code. See the code of the output and how it works and learn how to be a web developer. Gain clicks by clicking the button in the output and spend them to change the code like adding HTML, changing the JavaScript (like getting more clicks every time you click), and adding styles in CSS. See the console at the bottom of the screen where your achievements are. After you get 10 million clicks, you can unlock the terminal and install packages that enhance your program.', 'Use the left mouse button to gain clicks and upgrade codes.', 'enc0de6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:14', '2022-08-08 16:31:14', NULL),
(8329, 'Miner Cat 4', 'miner-cat-4', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 357, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/miner-cat-4/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Miner Cat 4 is a side-view Minecraft-inspired game with a Scratch cat character!\n', '\nMove: AD or left and right arrow keys\nJump: W or up arrow key or spacebar\nTalk to Bob: F\nSelect items: 1-6\nUse items: left mouse button\nDrop items: Q\nInventory: E\nPause: P\n', 'miner-cat-4.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:15', '2022-08-08 16:31:15', NULL),
(8330, 'Kogama Roller Coaster World', 'kogama-roller-coaster-world', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 1029, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kogama-roller-coaster-world/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Based in the pixelated world of Kogama, this game allows you to ride rollercoasters! With Minecraft-inspired 3D graphics and smooth gameplay, Kogama Roller Coaster World is a whole lot of fun. Enter the theme park and choose from a variety of different rollercoasters.', '', 'kogama-roller-coaster-worldd.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:15', '2022-08-08 16:31:15', NULL),
(8331, 'Super PSTW Adventure RPG', 'super-pstw-adventure-rpg', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 624, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/super-pstw-adventure-rpg/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Super PSTW Adventure RPG is', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Super Press Space to Win Adventure RPG is a pixelated game where your main goal is to rescue the princess who was kidnapped. The rule is simple, just press space!', 'Use space for everything.', 'super-pstw-adventure-rpg7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:16', '2022-08-08 16:31:16', NULL),
(8332, 'Jumphobia', 'jumphobia', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 359, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/jumphobia/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In Jumphobia, a new game made by Wix Games, you set out on an epic jumping adventure. You automatically jump when you run off a ledge. There are checkpoints flags along the way which will turn out to be useful... Jump on a monsters head to kill it.', '', 'jumphobiaa.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:17', '2022-08-08 16:31:17', NULL),
(8333, 'LinQuest', 'linquest', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 874, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/linquest/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'NoaDev.PlatformWeb browser (desktop and mobile)', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'LinQuest is a 2D platformer game with a mission to help adventurer Lin to search for a mysterious treasure in 3 different dangerous zones.', '\nA, D, or arrow keys to move.\nW, H, Up Arrow key, or space bar to jump\n', 'linquest2.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:17', '2022-08-08 16:31:17', NULL),
(8334, 'The Secret of the Necromancer', 'the-secret-of-the-necromancer', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 933, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/the-secret-of-the-necromancer/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Secret of the Necromancer is a scary point-and-click adventure game with beautiful graphics.\n', '', 'the-secret-of-the-necromancerr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:18', '2022-08-08 16:31:18', NULL),
(8335, 'The Illusionist\'s Dream', 'the-illusionist-s-dream', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 899, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/the-illusionist-s-dream/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'The Illusionist\'s Dream is', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Illusionist\'s Dream is a platforming game that takes you on an emotional adventure of an illusionist that stopped performing magic when his wife died. One night, he dreams of a world that was seemingly conjured by his wife, and she guides you as you slowly go through it. Will this dream help you overcome your grief? Find out in The Illusionist\'s Dream.', '\nArrow keys = move\nA = transform\nS = revert to human form\n', 'the-illusionist-s-dream9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:19', '2022-08-08 16:31:19', NULL),
(11809, 'Slot Car Racing', 'slot-car-racing', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 1116, '0', 'https://www.y8.com/embed/slot_car_racing', 'https://y8.com', 'en', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reaching the finish line sometimes isn’t all that simple. Look for ways how to get on top of your opponent. Start playing and show everyone your skills. The track has many crossings, so take care not to hit any of your opponents while getting through them. An accident would mean game over. Win the cup and get put into the hall of fame.', '', 'slot-car-racingl.gif', 1, 1, '2022-08-21 11:11:07', '2022-08-21 11:11:07', NULL),
(8337, 'The Explorer', 'the-explorer', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 17, 872, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/the-explorer/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'jhilven.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Explorer is an adventure-platformer game that sets in an alien world. You have landed your ship in a mysterious alien world, go explore this mystic island and defeat the evil monsters you encounter.\n', '\nMove: A and D\nJump: spacebar\nCrouch: S\n', 'the-explorer4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:19', '2022-08-08 16:31:19', NULL),
(8338, 'Knightin\'', 'knightin', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 1173, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/knightin/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Knightin\' is an adventure of a brave knight. Slay dangerous monsters and solve tricky puzzles to get your fame and glory in this dungeon-crawler adventure game. This game is the winner of Pixel Day 2018.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nSpace bar to interact\nZ or J to attack\n', 'knightin7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:20', '2022-08-08 16:31:20', NULL),
(8339, 'Sausage Dog', 'sausage-dog', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 11, 986, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/sausage-dog/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Functu', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sausage Dog is an adventure game to make the sausage dog go back home safely where its puppy is waiting. Explore the world and pass through each level by overcoming the obstacles. Collect the food and items along the way.', 'Use the arrow keys to move.', 'sausage-dog.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:21', '2022-08-08 16:31:21', NULL),
(8340, 'iF Idle Pirates Story', 'if-idle-pirates-story', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 1120, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/if-idle-pirates-story-ball-blast-gems/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'superpinman1.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a fun pirate-based idle game. Mine gems and build your town.\n', '', 'if-idle-pirates-story9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:21', '2022-08-08 16:31:21', NULL),
(8341, 'Monster Basement', 'monster-basement', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 417, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/monster-basement/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Godlimations.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Monster Basement is a room escape game with a scary atmosphere. You suddenly woke up in a mysterious room with creepy objects. Search the room thoroughly for clues and solve the puzzles before the monster returns. Do not miss a single thing as it can be an important clue. Can you successfully escape?\n', '', 'monster-basement2.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:22', '2022-08-08 16:31:22', NULL),
(8342, 'Goime 500', 'goime-500', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 1124, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/goime-500/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Goime 500 is a platformer game with 500 achievements to unlock. How far can you achieve?', 'Use arrow keys to move and shift to move slowly.', 'goime-5006.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:22', '2022-08-08 16:31:22', NULL),
(8343, 'Magic Maze', 'magic-maze', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 1163, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/magic-maze/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'aleksbog.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Magic Maze is an adventure game of a rat in a magical world of labyrinths where evil has awakened and is trying to enslave everyone. Your goal is to stop evil by collecting items, fighting in the arena, and going through labyrinths to collect all artifacts and punish the villain.', '\nWASD or arrow keys = move\nSpace = jump\nLeft-click = interact\n', 'magic-maze.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:23', '2022-08-08 16:31:23', NULL),
(8344, 'ANOVA', 'anova', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 146, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/anova/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ANOVA is a beautifully-designed point-and-click game that tells a story about a spirited pirate, Violet and her faithful robot companion, Tink.\n', '', 'anova7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:23', '2022-08-08 16:31:23', NULL),
(8345, 'Kill the Ice Age Baby Adventure', 'kill-the-ice-age-baby-adventure', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 326, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kill-the-ice-age-baby-adventure/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Kill the Ice Age Baby Adventure is', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kill the Ice Age Baby Adventure is an adventure game featuring a lot of memes and a lot of humor. Embark on an epic adventure to defeat the evil Ice Age Baby.', '\nWASD or arrow keys = move\nSpace = jump\nLeft-click = interact\nShift = sprint\n', 'kill-the-ice-age-baby-adventure6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:24', '2022-08-08 16:31:24', NULL),
(8346, 'Kity Builder', 'kity-builder', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 256, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kity-builder/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Sambero, irx99, Yeray Toledano,', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kity Builder is an adventure game to design and build your big city on a beautiful island.\n', '\nWASD - Move Kity\nMoving Mouse - Rotate camera\nSpacebar - Jump / Use Inventory item\nShift - Change mode (Exploration / Construction)\nP - Photo Mode\nLeft Click - Use inventory item / Take Photo\nScroll Mouse Wheel - Navigate Inventory (Up/Down)\n', 'kity-builder.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:25', '2022-08-08 16:31:25', NULL),
(8347, 'Pixel Cave', 'pixel-cave', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 477, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pixel-cave/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pixel Cave is a roguelike dungeon exploration game. The game features about 25 enemies and 8 enemies. It has randomly generated levels! The game was made by Megabyte.', '', 'pixel-cavee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:25', '2022-08-08 16:31:25', NULL),
(8348, 'The House', 'the-house', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 18, 121, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/the-house/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The House is an interesting point-and-click adventure game.\n', '', 'the-house1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:26', '2022-08-08 16:31:26', NULL),
(8349, 'Once Upon A Coma', 'once-upon-a-coma', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 1038, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/once-upon-a-coma/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Once Upon A Coma is an adventure game where you play as a character named Pete. Pete has just woken up from a coma and the world that he once knew has long gone and transformed into something dark and mysterious. The world is very different and strange and you must explore to find your way around the new city.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nX to swing the sword\nZ to jump\nSpace bar to interact\n', 'once-upon-a-comab.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:26', '2022-08-08 16:31:26', NULL),
(8350, 'Crypt Shyfter: Moonbright', 'crypt-shyfter-moonbright', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 1143, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/crypt-shyfter-moonbright/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Kung Fu Space Barbarian.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Crypt Shyfter: Moonbright is the exciting sequel to the popular Frostfall RPG. As you start your adventure you must choose which type of magical creature you wish to be - choices include a fairy, vampire and leonin. Your choice will affect your statistics i.e. a Reptiod has +1 attack strength. You can then choose different accessories to boost your power and weapons - each of these items affects your characters overall performance.\n', '', 'crypt-shyfter-moonbrightt.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:27', '2022-08-08 16:31:27', NULL),
(8351, 'Creative Kill Chamber', 'creative-kill-chamber', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 1161, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/creative-kill-chamber/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Creative Kill Chamber is a point-and-click adventure with a mission to escape a secure facility filled with heavily armed enemies. As the title says though, you\'re going to have to be creative in your methods. You need to be able to come up with quick solutions to all of the (probably deadly) problems presented to you. Use anything and everything you can find around you to make sure you get out of there in one piece!', 'Click/tap on the items/people on the screen to interact with them.', 'creative-kill-chamber7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:28', '2022-08-08 16:31:28', NULL),
(8352, 'Weird Bunny Banana', 'weird-bunny-banana', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 711, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/weird-bunny-banana/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Pixel Perfect Studio.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a challenging platformer for tough players. For every 2 kisses from the bunny on the stages, you will gain a permanent life. This is an arcade-style game where you\'ll have to start from the beginning if you lose all your lives. You gain extra lives for 100 bananas, 15000 points, or grabbing hamburgers. 3 worlds available for you!\n', '', 'weird-bunny-banana.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:28', '2022-08-08 16:31:28', NULL),
(8353, 'Adventure Boy: Jailbreak', 'adventure-boy-jailbreak', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 952, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/adventure-boy-jailbreak/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Adventure Boy: Jailbreak is', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Jailbreak is the second episode of the Adventure Boy series where you control Benson, the broke but resourceful kid on a mission to break your friend out of jail using nothing but the junk you can scrape up around town. A huge cast of funny, weird and thoughtful characters await you, with custom responses to nearly every permutation of items. Can you find the secret room?', '\nWASD = move\nShift = run\nZ + X = select items\nSpace = talk, use items\nEsc = pause\nM = mute\n', 'adventure-boy-jailbreak.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:29', '2022-08-08 16:31:29', NULL),
(8354, 'GroundBreaker', 'groundbreaker', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 279, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/groundbreaker/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Delunado.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'GroundBreaker is a mining game with the objective to reach the end of the dark mine. Collect rocks, find, and buy upgrades to help you in this mine journey. Defeat dangerous enemies and always be careful with your oxygen supply.', '\nWASD / arrow keys = move\nLeft-click = mine.\n', 'groundbreaker.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:30', '2022-08-08 16:31:30', NULL),
(8355, 'Diggy 2', 'diggy-2', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 13, 698, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/diggy-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Diggy 2 is a mining game in which you collect ore, fossils, and other valuable items. After each day, you can upgrade your equipment with the money that you have earned.', '', 'diggy-22.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:30', '2022-08-08 16:31:30', NULL),
(8356, 'Forward', 'forward', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 116, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/forward/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Christophe Coyard', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Forward is a card-based adventure game to slay as many monsters as you can.', 'Drag the left mouse button to move your hero card.', 'forward5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:31', '2022-08-08 16:31:31', NULL),
(8357, 'Kogama 4 Players Parkour', 'kogama-4-players-parkour', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 146, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kogama-4-player-parkour/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Onlydie', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kogama 4 Players Parkour is another game by Kogama. This time you need to beat a series of parkour challenges. You can join a team and compete with other teams to be the first to reach the flag. The environments are difficult, and you must maneuver swiftly to avoid any hazardous obstacles. Reach the checkpoint to save your current progress so that you can always respawn in the location. You can also use the block gun to place blocks to help you on your journey, but be careful as it has limited ammo. Work together with your teammates to reach the flag faster. If you want some other challenges, play some fun mini-games!', '', 'kogama-4-players-parkour5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:32', '2022-08-08 16:31:32', NULL),
(8358, 'Arkandian Crusade', 'arkandian-crusade', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 59, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/arkandian-crusade/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Terry and Keir Brown.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Explore dungeons from the top down using the arrow keys, and slay foes by selecting attacks with your mouse in this light-hearted fantasy RPG. Collect treasure, complete quests, and advance in your character class in classic fantasy RPG style.\n', '\nArrow keys to move\nLeft mouse button to interact\n', 'arkandian-crusadee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:33', '2022-08-08 16:31:33', NULL),
(8359, 'Nevermore', 'nevermore', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 724, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/nevermore/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Nevermore was', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nevermore is a platform game where you collect all the blue coins as you travel around in the wonderful world of Nevermore.', '\nLeft and right arrow keys = move\nSpace = jump (hold to jump higher)\n', 'nevermore4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:33', '2022-08-08 16:31:33', NULL),
(8360, '2020 Game', '2020-game', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 1147, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/2020-game/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Game 2020 is an adventure game that puts players through all the major events that happened in 2020, such as the Australia wildfires, Covid-19, the rise of TikTok, etc.\n', '\nAD or left and right arrows to move\nW or up arrow key or space bar to jump\n', '2020-game4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:34', '2022-08-08 16:31:34', NULL),
(8361, 'Monster Clearer', 'monster-clearer', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 322, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/monster-clearer/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Adventale, a very talented young game developer who creates innovative and artistic RPG games.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Monster Clearer is an innovative RPG with simple mechanics but an addictive gameplay.\n', '', 'monster-clearerr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:35', '2022-08-08 16:31:35', NULL),
(8362, 'Beyond Eden', 'beyond-eden', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 281, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/beyond-eden/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'ItsNotSimon.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Beyond Eden is an adventure game in which you control a character that needs to deal with various choices on his journey to utopia.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nSpace bar to interact\nLeft mouse button to choose\n', 'beyond-eden6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:35', '2022-08-08 16:31:35', NULL),
(8363, 'Monster Breeder', 'monster-breeder', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 139, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/monster-breeder/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Neil Cicierega, an American Internet polymath. You can support him on Patreon or Paypal.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Monster Breeder is a fantastic adventure game that combines text-based gameplay together with rogue elements and RTS mechanics. You are a monster breeder and you scour the world to find new and interesting monsters to capture and breed – you want to find as many new species as possible and become the most decorated hunter in the land.', '\nLeft click to choose an option\nArrow keys to navigate an area\n', 'monster-breederr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:36', '2022-08-08 16:31:36', NULL),
(8364, 'Gelda', 'gelda', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 73, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/gelda/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Netflix\'s series, Hilda.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gelda is a young girl who is seeking for adventure! In this story, Gelda is traveling through the wilderness – she is accompanied by her faithful companion Abi. Together, you must complete a range of challenges and try to defeat various monsters.\n', '', 'geldaa.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:37', '2022-08-08 16:31:37', NULL),
(8365, 'Crypt Shyfter: Limerick', 'crypt-shyfter-limerick', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 424, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/crypt-shyfter-limerick/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Kung Fu Space Barbarian.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Crypt Shyfter: Limerick is the text-based story game based in the wild west era. You must settle every decision using force and muscle as that is all that people understand in this time period. You are given to become a hero and restore order to the land based on the decisions that you make at every opportunity.\n', '', 'crypt-shyfter-limerickk.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:37', '2022-08-08 16:31:37', NULL),
(8366, 'Mine Clone', 'mine-clone', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 1037, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mine-clone/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Girts Kesteris (Sacristan).', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mine Clone is a cool Minecraft inspired game in which you can use your creativity to build whatever you can imagine! You can interact with this blocky world and build different blocks – create structures, cities – anything!\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nMouse scroll up to switch weapons\nLeft mouse button to attack\nE to open the inventory\nRight mouse button to place an item\nSpace bar to jump\nF to open the task menu\n1234 to use accessory\nEsc to open the menu\n', 'mine-clone.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:37', '2022-08-08 16:31:37', NULL),
(8367, 'Trader of Stories: Chapter 2', 'trader-of-stories-chapter-2', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 524, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/trader-of-stories-chapter-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Rudowski brothers. Support the developer on Patreon.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The story of Trader of Stories continues. Help Little Willow to find the truth and the answer she seeks.\n', '\nLeft click to interact\nSpace bar or H to show hints\nI to open inventory\n', 'trader-of-stories-chapter-25.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:38', '2022-08-08 16:31:38', NULL),
(8368, 'The Lion Guard: Assemble', 'the-lion-guard-assemble', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 241, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/the-lion-guard-assemble/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In The Lion Guard: Assemble you set out on an adventure across the African Savanna with Kion, the son of Simba and Nala! Run and jump across hills, trees, and valleys. Can you manage to free Ono and Jasiri?\n', '', 'the-lion-guard-assemble4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:38', '2022-08-08 16:31:38', NULL),
(8369, 'Home Is Where The Hearth Is', 'home-is-where-the-hearth-is', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 988, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/home-is-where-the-hearth-is/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home is Where the Hearth Is, a fun game of survival. You are stranded on an island, isolated from the world. The cold is seeping in and it is snowing! You must do what you can to survive and keep the fire lit.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nSpace bar to interact\n', 'home-is-where-the-hearth-is5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:38', '2022-08-08 16:31:38', NULL),
(8370, 'Rubber Dinghy', 'rubber-dinghy', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 260, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/rubber-dinghy/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Kurt Hodges.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You are stranded on a desert island after an exhausting day of rowing in your dinghy. Your dinghy is badly damaged so you must find a way to repair it to return to civilization! Throughout the island you will find various objects that you can use and harvest. Furthermore, you can also interact with animals such as crabs and other survivors. By using logic, and the items at your disposal, you must complete a series of different tasks such as fixing the broken bridge and helping crabs in their fight to the death.\n', '\nWASD to move\nE to interact\n', 'rubber-dinghyy.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:39', '2022-08-08 16:31:39', NULL),
(8371, 'Désiré Chapter I', 'desire-chapter-i', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 756, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/desire/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Sylvain Seccia.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Desire is an intriguing game and the first chapter of this interesting series. The game takes a click and point style mechanism, and you must move through the story with various characters. It is an emotional story, and you will find yourself wrapped up in the events that unfold.\n', '', 'desire-chapter-ie.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:39', '2022-08-08 16:31:39', NULL),
(8372, 'Simpocalypse', 'simpocalypse', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 276, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/simpocalypse/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'GamexGames.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Simpocalypse is an in-depth post-apocalyptic civilization simulator game with an idle element.\n', '', 'simpocalypse.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:40', '2022-08-08 16:31:40', NULL),
(8373, 'Curiophillia', 'curiophillia', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 580, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/curiophillia/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Daniel Graves.', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Curiophillia is an adventure game to mine and discovers various artifacts throughout the island. Complete your Grandpa\'s journal and discover as many artifacts as you can.\n', '\nWASD to move\nClick to interact\nE to open your journal\nQ to place bomb\n', 'curiophillia.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:41', '2022-08-08 16:31:41', NULL);
