(8395, 'Doodle Creatures', 'doodle-creatures', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 183, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/doodle-creatures/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 22, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What happens if you combine an elephant with a flamingo? In Doodle Creatures you can find out as you create hundreds of fantastic and unique creatures by combining different animals. Play doctor and scan hundreds of animals DNA which allows you to combine different animal traits to create new creatures! ', '', 'doodle-creaturess.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:31:54', '2022-08-08 16:31:54', NULL),
