(8524, 'Parkour Race: Nyan Cat', 'parkour-race-nyan-cat', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 299, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/parkour-race-nyan-cat-multiplayer-medium/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Ratten (Adventure Box).', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Parkour Race: Nyan Cat is a cool and challenging parkour race in a colorful world of Nyan Cat. First to reach the winner-sign wins! An additional challenge: Find the secret code on top of the Nyan Cat sign!\n', '\nWASD to move\nLeft click on the mouse to strike\nSpacebar to jump\nShift to run and jump longer\n', 'parkour-race-nyan-cat.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:16', '2022-08-08 16:33:16', NULL),
(8525, 'Ski FRVR', 'ski-frvr', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 120, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ski-frvr/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Chris Benjaminsen.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ski FRVR is a sports game that focus on downslope skiing, and it\'s as relaxing as it is really fun. There\'s no real goal ahead of you, just keep skiing until you get to the end, and that\'s it. Along the way, you\'ll be given objectives which will score you some gold, which you can then use to buy different skis available at the shop. As you go downhill, you\'ll be scored for the distance you\'ve went through, so the score also increases as you go faster. There\'s no rush though, you can slow down the pace to collect everything along the slope, as well as do stunts, to gain even more points.\n', 'Tap/click and swipe to the direction you\'d like your skier to go.', 'ski-frvr4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:16', '2022-08-08 16:33:16', NULL),
(8526, 'TapBasket', 'tapbasket', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 305, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tapbasketball/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Youdevice!.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'TapBasket is a fun basketball game in which you only have three chances to jump and score. Love this kind of game? You should also check Tap-Tap Shots.\n', '\nPress left/right arrow or left mouse button to jump\nPress space bar to restart\n', 'tapbasket.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:17', '2022-08-08 16:33:17', NULL),
(8527, 'Stickman Beach Volleyball', 'stickman-beach-volleyball', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 755, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stickman-beach-volleyball/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Yuriy Nikshych. Also, check out the stickman tennis game in Stickman Tennis 3D.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This is a fun stickman beach volleyball game! Smash the ball perfectly and win the matches.\n', '\nWASD and arrow keys: move\nVolley and Lob (hit the ball): X and Z\n', 'stickman-beach-volleyball.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:18', '2022-08-08 16:33:18', NULL),
(8528, 'Japanese Baseball', 'japanese-baseball', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 1034, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/japanese-baseball/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Is there anything more Japanese than a cute little cat playing baseball? This little game named Japanese Baseball is exactly that! Play as a cat with a bat that\'s just waiting to hit a home run. It\'s easy, it\'s simple, and it\'s 100% fun. If you think it\'s too easy, you can even pick a difficulty before you start. Batter up!\n', '', 'japanese-baseball1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:19', '2022-08-08 16:33:19', NULL),
(8529, 'Waterpark Parkour!', 'waterpark-parkour', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 240, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/waterpark-parkour/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Genard (Adventure Box).', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The jumpmaster invites you to his new and challenging Waterpark Parkour. Find flags around the park to complete the game!', '\nWASD to move\nHold Shiftto jump longer\n1-4 to use equipment\nI to open inventory\nSpace bar to jump\nLeft mouse button to shoot\n', 'waterpark-parkour.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:19', '2022-08-08 16:33:19', NULL),
(8530, 'Pool Rush FRVR', 'pool-rush-frvr', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 15, 250, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pool-rush-frvr/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pool Rush FRVR is a pool game that doesn\'t go by your conventional pool rules. The only goal in this game is to shoot as many balls as you can into the side pockets. You\'ll have a limited number of shots (indicated by the number on your cue ball), and once it turns to 0, you\'ll lose a ball. If you don\'t have an extra ball, it\'s game over (you get extra balls by making sure all balls on a table are shot into pockets).\n', 'Click/tap and drag from the cue ball to one direction. Let go to fling the ball into the opposite direction (there will also be an arrow guiding you to the direction the ball will go to).', 'pool-rush-frvr1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:20', '2022-08-08 16:33:20', NULL),
(8531, 'SPORTS', 'sports', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 915, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/sports/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Innersloth for Ludum Dare Game Jam 41. You can follow the developer on Twitter for more updates.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'SPORTS is an awesome soccer game with a twist – in this title you control a single character on a soccer team and you must try and score as many goals as possible in the given time-frame. This soccer match differs from the standard format however as you are equipped with various weapons and you must use these to try and smash your opponents into a bloody pulp!\n', '\nWASD/arrows to move\nE/Shift to switch character\nSpace to attack\nP to pause/skip cutscene\n', 'sportss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:21', '2022-08-08 16:33:21', NULL),
(8532, 'Curling FRVR', 'curling-frvr', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 336, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/curling-frvr/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Chris Benjaminsen.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Curling FRVR is a sports game where you throw a stone and let it slide along the ice. Your main goal is to let the stone slide all the way to the other side of the area where there\'s a target. You\'ll have to land the stone somewhere inside that target. It sounds easy enough, but there are a few things that will make this difficult. First, you\'ll have to take a good guess how much power you\'ll be using to throw the stone - if it\'s too much, you\'ll overshoot, if it\'s too weak, you won\'t even reach the target. There will also be other stones near the target that might hinder your plans - sometimes though, there will be stones that are the same color as you. If you hit these stones and they land on the target as well, it\'ll be added to your score.\n', 'Tap the screen/Use your left mouse button to control the strength of your throw. You\'ll also use the same control to help glide your stone to the target area.', 'curling-frvr4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:21', '2022-08-08 16:33:21', NULL),
(8533, 'Parkour Race: Proto', 'parkour-race-proto', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 600, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/parkour-race-proto-hard-2-player/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Ratten (Adventure Box).', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Parkour Race: Proto is a multiplayer parkour racing game from Adventure Box. Be the first one to reach the finish area and press the button!\n', '\nWASD to move\nLeft click on the mouse to strike\nSpace bar to jump\nShift to run and jump longer\n', 'parkour-race-proto.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:22', '2022-08-08 16:33:22', NULL),
(8534, 'Boomerang Sports', 'boomerang-sports', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 612, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/boomerang-sports/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Boomerang Sports allows you take control of your favourite Cartoon Network characters including Tom and Jerry, Daffy Duck, Bugs Bunny and Shaggy and Scooby. You must compete in various sporting events to be crowned the champion; these sports include basketball, water pogo and donut boat racing.\n', '', 'boomerang-sportss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:22', '2022-08-08 16:33:22', NULL),
(8535, 'HitBoxing', 'hitboxing', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 941, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hitboxing/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'HitBoxing is a fun physics-based boxing game. Do your best to land powerful punches and take down the opponents.', 'Use the WASD keys or the arrow keys or drag left mouse button to do actions.', 'hitboxing3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:23', '2022-08-08 16:33:23', NULL),
(8536, 'BrawlBall.io', 'brawlball-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 1135, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/brawlball-io-tas/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'BrawlBall.io was', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'BrawlBall.io is a multiplayer 2D pixel soccer game with simple controls.', '\nMove: WASD\nAim direction: mouse\nShoot/tackle: left mouse button\n', 'brawlball-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:24', '2022-08-08 16:33:24', NULL),
(8537, 'Table Tennis Challenge', 'table-tennis-challenge', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 11, 189, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/table-tennis-challenge/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Table Tennis Challenge is a sports game where you play as a rising ping pong star! Start learning the ropes of the game in your garage as you play with a friend, then move on to tournaments with professional players as you grow as a player. Earn coins that\'ll let you buy better paddles to defeat even better opponents around the world.', 'Mouse cursor = move the paddle', 'table-tennis-challenge3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:24', '2022-08-08 16:33:24', NULL),
(8538, 'Basketball Arcade', 'basketball-arcade', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 16, 277, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/basketball-arcade/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Basketball Arcade is the sports arcade game in which you can prove your basketball skills by making shots from all different distances. Start by selecting your favorite team and making shots before the time runs out. Make as many as you can to get a high score that you can be proud of.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to control the character\'s movement\nLock cursor = F\nUnlock cursor = Esc\nJump = space bar\nShoot = left click\nOptions = O\n', 'basketball-arcadee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:25', '2022-08-08 16:33:25', NULL),
(8541, '3D Bowling', '3d-bowling', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 944, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/3d-bowling/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, '3D Bowling is the 3D bowling game in which you can play the classic family game that we have all grown up to love. Have unlimited bowling fun in this online version, you practice your lines and aim to try and get that infamous strike by knocking all of the pins down in one go. You can play a single game on your own to try and beat your score or you can play against a friend in local play as you take turns.\n', '', '3d-bowlingg.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:26', '2022-08-08 16:33:26', NULL),
(8542, 'Free Kick Classic (3D Free Kick)', 'free-kick-classic-3d-free-kick', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 718, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/free-kick-classic/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Free Kick Classic (3D Free Kick) is the totally immersive free kick simulation game in which you will stand over a soccer ball with a wall of towering defenders and an acrobatic goalkeeper trying t stop you. Take a deep breath, take your aim and curl the ball into the back of the net with style as you swerve the ball in midflight to clear the wall and outsmart the keeper.\n', '', 'free-kick-classic-3d-free-kickc.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:26', '2022-08-08 16:33:26', NULL),
(8543, 'Head World Cup', 'head-world-cup', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 946, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/head-world-cup/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Faramel Games.', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Head World Cup is the soccer arcade game in which you will select your favorite player from your favorite team and head to the world cup – quite literally. Using your oversized head, you most position your player under the ball and try to score against your opponent.\n', '\nLeft and right arrow to move\nSpace bar to jump\n', 'head-world-cupp.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:27', '2022-08-08 16:33:27', NULL),
(8546, 'Euro Soccer Sprint', 'euro-soccer-sprint', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 17, 870, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/euro-soccer-sprint/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Run as far as you can in this soccer themed endless runner!', '', 'euro-soccer-sprintt.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:33:29', '2022-08-08 16:33:29', NULL);
