(8657, 'Hipster vs Rockers', 'hipster-vs-rockers', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 839, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hipster-vs-rockers/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Go Panda Games.', 26, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gaia, Ero, and Ai are best friends forever. They like to try the latest fashion and compare it with each other that suits them. This time they try the style of rockers and hipsters. Wonder which fashion is suitable for them?\n', '', 'hipster-vs-rockers6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:34:29', '2022-08-08 16:34:29', NULL),
