(8980, 'N Game', 'n-game', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 1065, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/n-game/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'N Game was', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'N Game is a platformer that lets you play as a dude who has the athletic ability of a ninja and can do almost anything, but it\'s accompanied by a very short lifespan - like, 15-minute short. You need to finish a set amount of levels before your 15-minute timer goes down to 0, or you will die. You need to finish each level by pushing a button to open a door, and heading to that door to exit it. A lot of gold can also be scattered in each level, so getting them would be really helpful too. ', 'Make sure to also read the tips under Help in the main menu to find different maneuvers that\'ll help you get around each level more efficiently', 'n-game0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:37:46', '2022-08-08 16:37:46', NULL),
