(9081, 'Replaying The Game', 'replaying-the-game', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 839, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/replaying-the-game/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Nutcase Nightmare', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Replaying The Game is a sequel game from The Game. It\'s a funny random meme game where you can unlock funny animation in each level.', '\nLeft and right arrow = move\nUp arrow = jump\nDown arrow = duck\nLeft-click = interact with the buttons\n', 'replaying-the-game7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:07', '2022-08-08 16:39:07', NULL),
(9082, 'Bed and Breakfast 3', 'bed-and-breakfast-3', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 173, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bed-and-breakfast-3/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bed and Breakfast 3 is a hotel management game that lets you run your own little hotel and make money off of it. Use your hospitality skills to give your customers the best hotel experience of their life. Cook the best food, prepare the best beds, and keep your hotel in tip top shape so everyone can enjoy it, and in return, you get more money to make your hotel even better!', 'Click/tap on the services/areas you need to go to, and your manager will automatically work it for you', 'bed-and-breakfast-37.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:08', '2022-08-08 16:39:08', NULL),
(9083, 'Synopsis Quest', 'synopsis-quest', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 386, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/synopsis-quest/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'the Demon Lord? Take on the awesome adventure of Synopsis Quest to find out!', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Synopsis Quest is a collection of mini-games that lets you play as a hero with only one goal in mind, and that\'s to save the world. You\'ll do this by clearing a bunch of quick games that\'ll give you one thing to do. Once completed, you can move on to the next challenge. You\'ll keep doing this until the world is safe from the hands of the Demon Lord.\n', '\nArrow keys = Move\nSpace = Inspect/Talk\n', 'synopsis-quest5.JPG', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:08', '2022-08-08 16:39:08', NULL),
(9084, 'Big ICE Tower Tiny Square', 'big-ice-tower-tiny-square', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 828, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/big-ice-tower-tiny-square/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'single-screen arcade games. The game is one giant level broken up into large single-screen sections.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Big ICE Tower Tiny Square is the next episode of Big Tower Tiny Square, a pixel-platformer game in a maze-like giant ice tower, with a very wide view!\n', 'Press spacebar or A button (controller) to start.', 'big-ice-tower-tiny-square.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:09', '2022-08-08 16:39:09', NULL),
(9085, 'Red.', 'red', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 507, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/red-1/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Red. is a defense game from IvoryDrive in which you need to survive as long as possible to shoot away the incoming black circles.\n', '\nLeft mouse button to shoot\nSpace bar to do power shots\nP to pause the game\n', 'red0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:10', '2022-08-08 16:39:10', NULL),
(9086, 'Area Raiders', 'area-raiders', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 1101, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/area-raiders/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'GamexGames, the same developer behind War Clicks.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Area Raiders is an interesting idle game to storm Area 51 to rescue the aliens and reveal the hidden secrets.\n', '', 'area-raiders.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:11', '2022-08-08 16:39:11', NULL),
(9087, 'Pandemic 2', 'pandemic-2', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 959, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pandemic-2/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Dark Realm Studios.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In Pandemic 2, you need to manage a disease (including naming your own disease, like Coronavirus) with a goal to infect all the people in the world!\n', '', 'pandemic-25.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:12', '2022-08-08 16:39:12', NULL),
(9088, 'Cookin\'Truck', 'cookin-truck', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 784, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cookin-truck/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Spirkop.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Manage your food truck business and try to become the best in the class!\n', '\nPress left mouse button to interact\nPress WASD or drag the left mouse button to move the camera view\n', 'cookin-truck3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:13', '2022-08-08 16:39:13', NULL),
(9089, 'Stack Shot', 'stack-shot', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 18, 1156, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stack-shot/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stack Shot is a brilliant arcade game that is similar to the hugely popular Fire Balls 3D. In this game, you must fire the balls at the towering stack in the center of each level – you must time your shots carefully to avoid the barriers that are continually spinning.\n', '\nPress left mouse button to shoot\nPress right mouse button to use the bomb\n', 'stack-shott.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:13', '2022-08-08 16:39:13', NULL),
(9090, 'Bounce Floor', 'bounce-floor', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 953, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bounce-floor/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Bounce Floor was', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bounce Floor is a fun game in which you take on the role of a bouncer in a night club! You must keep everyone safe and try to get rid of the criminals and thugs who are trying to steal and cause problems! You must talk to the people within the building and try to obtain information about the criminals. ', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nSpace bar to interact/kick out\nEsc to pause\n', 'bounce-floorr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:14', '2022-08-08 16:39:14', NULL),
(9091, 'Air Wings - Missile Attack', 'air-wings-missile-attack', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 583, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/air-wings-missile-attack/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Air Wings - Missile Attack is a fun missile dodging game in an airplane! The missiles are coming from different directions and you must swiftly maneuver to avoid and make them hit each other. There are several power-ups that you can pick, like stars to increase your score and shield to protect from missile\'s damage. How long can you fly? Have fun!\n', 'Use AD or left/right arrow to control the airplane.', 'air-wings-missile-attackk.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:15', '2022-08-08 16:39:15', NULL),
(9092, 'Portal: The Flash Version', 'portal-the-flash-version', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 307, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/portal-the-flash-version/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'We Create Stuff.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Portal: The Flash Version brings the epic console game straight to your web browser and mobile devices! If you haven’t heard of Portal then you are missing out! In this game, you use your special physics gun to create inter-dimensional portals in-between walls and objects. You must use these portals to navigate through a series of levels and challenges.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nLeft click to shoot portal\nQ to shoot blue portal\nE to shoot yellow portal\nR to reset portals\n', 'portal-the-flash-version5.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:15', '2022-08-08 16:39:15', NULL),
(9093, 'Supergun', 'supergun', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 873, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/supergun/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Aron Sommer.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Supergun is an intense and fast paced arcade game from the creators of the awesome Eagle Ride. In this title, you control a spaceship and your aim is to guide your ship through space and avoid the red squares. Your ship moves and fires automatically – all you have to do is control the left and right movements. This might sound easy but the gameplay is fast and you must have great reactions!\n', '', 'supergun.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:16', '2022-08-08 16:39:16', NULL),
(9094, 'Slightly Annoying Traffic', 'slightly-annoying-traffic', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 667, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/slightly-annoying-traffic/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Slightly Annoying Traffic is a fun and exciting traffic management game (yes traffic management can be fun!). You must take up the role of a traffic manager and take care of an intersection of traffic and ensure that all vehicles can cross the intersection safely without crashing! To control the traffic you must click on individual vehicles to stop them in their tracks.', 'Left click to make a vehicle stop.', 'slightly-annoying-trafficb.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:16', '2022-08-08 16:39:16', NULL),
(9095, 'Brick Breaker', 'brick-breaker', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 1175, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/brick-breaker-intergalactic/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Playtouch.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Brick Breaker is an awesome puzzle game with similarities to the iconic Super Breakout and Pong. You must control a paddleboard and use it to bounce a ball into various different shapes on each level. The graphics are cool and the gameplay uses a galactic theme – the balls look like shooting stars! Your paddle changes size and as you progress the gameplay becomes increasingly difficult.\n', 'Move your mouse to control the paddle\'s movement.', 'brick-breaker2.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:17', '2022-08-08 16:39:17', NULL),
(9096, 'Ping Pong Chaos', 'ping-pong-chaos', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 943, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ping-pong-chaos/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'New Eich Games.', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ping Pong Chaos is a chaotic 2-player game from the developer of Rooftop Snipers! Get ready to enter a crazy world and play insane ping pong matches against the computer or against your friends!\n', '', 'ping-pong-chaos5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:18', '2022-08-08 16:39:18', NULL),
(9097, 'Cursor * 10', 'cursor-10', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 1094, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cursor-10/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 31, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Use your 10 cursors to reach the 16th floor. As your previous lives are replayed, try to cooperate with yourself to reach the goal.\n', '', 'cursor-100.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:19', '2022-08-08 16:39:19', NULL),
(9099, 'Smash Karts', 'smash-karts', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 941, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/smash-karts/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'SmashKarts.io is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Smash Karts is a 3D multiplayer kart battle game. Drive your go-kart, pick up weapons, and blow up other karts to win! Keep playing to level up and unlock new characters and prizes.', '\nWASD or arrow keys to drive\nSpace to fire weapons\n', 'smash-karts.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:19', '2022-08-08 16:39:19', NULL),
(9100, 'Shell Shockers', 'shell-shockers', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 1167, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/shellshockersio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Shell Shockers is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shell Shockers (Shellshock.io) is a multiplayer .io FPS game featuring eggs armed with guns. You control one of these weapon-wielding eggs in one of four online game modes where the aim is to shatter your opponents with bullets and bombs. It\'s the ultimate online egg shooting game!', '\nGamepad is now supported!\nWASD to move\nLeft-click to shoot\nE to change weapon\nQ to throw a grenade\nR to reload\nSpace to jump\nShift to zoom and aim\n', 'shell-shockers.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:20', '2022-08-08 16:39:20', NULL),
(9101, 'Bloxd.io', 'bloxd-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 711, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bloxdhop-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Roblox’s Tower of Hell.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bloxd.io is an online game featuring Minecraft graphics and various game modes. The game modes feature parkour, sandbox creativity, and combat, depending on which mode you choose to play.', '\nWASD to move\nShift or double-tap W to run\nC, Z, \\, or Caps Lock to crouch\nT or Enter to chat\nB to open shop\n/ to start command\n', 'bloxd-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:20', '2022-08-08 16:39:20', NULL),
(9102, 'Ships 3D', 'ships-3d', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 218, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ships-3d/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ships 3D is an online naval warfare game featuring frantic frigate battles and chaotic smash-ups at sea. Join your friends in thrilling multiplayer ship wars featuring up to 20 players.', '\nWASD = move\nMouse = look around\nF = interact with steering, sail, and cannons when standing close to them.\n', 'ships-3d1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:21', '2022-08-08 16:39:21', NULL),
(9105, 'Stabfish 2', 'stabfish-2', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 646, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stabfish2-io-multiplayer/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Zytech AI', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stabfish 2 is the sequel of Stabfish.io, a shark fighting arena .io game. Battle other sharks in an online arena and impale as many as you can. This second installment features new sharks, abilities, loot, and much more.', '\nMouse = direct your weapon\nLeft-click and right-click = use skills\n', 'stabfish-2.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:23', '2022-08-08 16:39:23', NULL),
(9106, 'Zombs Royale (ZombsRoyale.io)', 'zombs-royale-zombsroyale-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 678, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/zombsroyaleio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Yang and Jeremiah under the name End Game.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zombs Royale is a multiplayer survival game set in a Battle Royale arena. As with many Battle Royale games, you join the deadly battlefield via parachute and scramble around looking for resources and comradery with other players. Build a base, fight zombie hordes, and take down hostile players. There can only be one Zombs champion!', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nM or Tab to view map\nE to interact\nLeft click to shoot\nRight click to open emoticon list\nR to reload\n', 'zombs-royale-zombsroyale-io2.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:23', '2022-08-08 16:39:23', NULL),
(9107, 'MiniGiants.io', 'minigiants-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 634, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/minigiants-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Niight Steed Games made MiniGiants.io. They also', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'MiniGiants.io is a top-down multiplayer deathmatch game. Take control of your own MiniGiant and battle other players for rewards. You can choose from several classes. As you level up, you\'ll grow larger, more powerful, and earn more loot to make your character stronger!', '\nPress the left mouse button to attack\nPress the right mouse button to boost your speed\n', 'minigiants-io5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:24', '2022-08-08 16:39:24', NULL),
(9108, 'Rocket Bot Royale', 'rocket-bot-royale', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 875, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/rocket-bot-royale/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Rocket Bot Royale is a gravity-defying multiplayer tank game set in a battle royale arena. Blast other players, collect coins, avoid the rising water levels, and survive for longer than the rest.', '\nA / left arrow key = move left\nD / right arrow key = move right\nMove mouse = aim\nLeft-click = shoot\n', 'rocket-bot-royale.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:25', '2022-08-08 16:39:25', NULL),
(9109, 'Pixel Warfare', 'pixel-warfare', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 16, 1128, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pixel-warfare/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Angel Hrisimov.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Pixel Warfare is a superb multiplayer FPS game featuring blocky graphics and 8-bit music. The gameplay is classic and tactical, featuring various weapons and maps. Choose a game in the menu to get started!', '\nUse the WASD or arrow keys to move around\nR to reload\n1-6 number keys to select your weapon\nPress the tab to go to the menu\n', 'pixel-warfare.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:25', '2022-08-08 16:39:25', NULL),
(9110, 'StarBlast', 'starblast', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 834, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/starblastio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'mining asteroids and destroying the ships of opposition forces. Just shoot rocks until they explode!', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'StarBlast is a fun multiplayer arcade shooter set in space. Mine asteroids and fight other players in your own fully upgradable spaceship. Work together with your teammates to ensure victory.', '\nArrow keys to drive\nLMB to shoot\n', 'starblast.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:26', '2022-08-08 16:39:26', NULL),
(9111, 'Merc Zone', 'merc-zone', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 586, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/merc-zone/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'pressing ‘play now’. If you want to play a custom game and select the desired mode and map, you can ', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Merc Zone is an online multiplayer FPS game made by Blue Wizard Digital. Find your favorite weapon and fight in various game modes and maps. This stylish suit-and-tie shooter features fast-paced action and a sleek 3D aesthetic that makes you want to play more!', '\nWASD to move \nE/mouse scroll to switch weapons\nSpace bar to jump\nF to interact \nR to reload\nG to throw grenades\nC/Shift to crouch \nLeft mouse button to shoot \nRight mouse button or X to aim\n', 'merc-zone4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:26', '2022-08-08 16:39:26', NULL),
(9112, 'EvoWorld.io (FlyOrDie.io)', 'evoworld-io-flyordie-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 1082, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/flyordieio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'EvoWorld.io is a multiplayer survival game previously known as FlyOrDie.io. You start as a small fly and level up as you eat more food. As you evolve, other players become part of your diet too. Each level comes with a new special ability and more things to eat. The choice is simple, you Fly or Die!', '\nWASD to move around\nLeft click to fly\n', 'evoworld-io-flyordie-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:27', '2022-08-08 16:39:27', NULL),
(9113, 'Taming.io', 'taming-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 1136, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/taming-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'LapaMauve', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Taming-io is a survival .io game with magical pets that fight by your side. Harvest resources and unlock upgrades as you age. Craft items, build a base, and battle other players and their pets to become the savviest survivor.', '\nWASD or ZQSD or arrow keys to move\nLeft mouse button to attack\n', 'taming-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:28', '2022-08-08 16:39:28', NULL),
(9114, 'Stabfish.io', 'stabfish-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 998, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stabfish-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'attacking from the side and behind. Each kill adds length to your tusk. Once your tusk is long enoug', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stabfish.io is a free io game where you play as a deadly oceanic beast. Join a multiplayer arena of fish equipped with fatal tusks and take down your share of prey while avoiding the sharp end of another player’s stabber. Collect the fish like trophies, eat food for boosts, and dominate the sea.', '\nMove your mouse to control the movement\nPress left mouse button to boost speed\n', 'stabfish-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:28', '2022-08-08 16:39:28', NULL),
(9116, 'BattleDudes.io', 'battledudes-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 994, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/battledudes-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Šarūnas Visockas', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'BattleDudes.io is a 2D multiplayer .io game with a fully destructible map. Fight other players using guns, tanks, and other destructive forces. There are multiple maps and game modes to play. Log in to earn XP and level up!', '\nWASD to move\nLeft mouse button to shoot\nR to reload\nE to enter vehicles\nMouse scroll or 1-4 number keys to switch weapons\nM or Tab to enlarge the map\nYou can customize the controls in the Settings\n', 'battledudes-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:29', '2022-08-08 16:39:29', NULL),
(9117, 'Gulper.io', 'gulper-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 861, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/gulper-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'gulping the glowing dots scattered around the map. You must move quickly and keep an eye out for ene', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gulper.io is an awesome multiplayer snake game that takes inspiration from Slither.io. You must take control of a small glowing worm and try to grow bigger so that you can destroy the other worms on the playing field.', 'Press left mouse button to boost speed at the cost of your size.', 'gulper-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:39:30', '2022-08-08 16:39:30', NULL);
