(9196, 'Schedios.io', 'schedios-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 535, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/schedios-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Applatoons.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Schedios.io is a multiplayer free drawing game in which a player draws a sketch while the rest of the players try their best to guess what is being drawn.\n', '\nUse the mouse to select an animal avatar and username of your choice\nUse the mouse to draw when it is your turn to draw\nUse brush to draw any color\nUse brush size to change from normal, thick and thicker brush sizes\nUse eraser to erase any part of the drawing\nUse flood fill to fill color in shapes\nUse clear to clear drawing i.e. start fresh\nUse undo to undo your last drawing action\nUse keyboard or touch (when onscreen-keyboard is on) to type and send you guesses\nClick on any other player\'s animal avatar to like/pat them\n', 'schedios-io0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:15', '2022-08-08 16:40:15', NULL),
(9197, 'Witz.io', 'witz-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 882, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/witz-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Witz.io is a multiplayer quiz game. Play with other players to write and vote for the answers.\n', '', 'witz-io6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:16', '2022-08-08 16:40:16', NULL),
(9198, 'Monarchies.io', 'monarchies-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 16, 997, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/monarchies-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Corey van Hoosen. This game is also known as Monarchies of Wax and Honey.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Monarchies.io is a multiplayer simulation game in which you become a queen honey bee who needs to command your workers to create a mighty army. You need to manage every aspect carefully, from gathering nectar to expanding the territory. Watch out for other bees and good luck!\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys or left mouse button to move or interact\nNumber keys to do actions\n', 'monarchies-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:16', '2022-08-08 16:40:16', NULL),
(9199, 'Doodlr.io', 'doodlr-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 226, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/doodlr-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Little Island Games.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Doodlr.io is an exciting 1 vs 1 drawing and guessing game. Connect with a random opponent from anywhere around the world, and unleash your inner artist!\n', '', 'doodlr-io6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:17', '2022-08-08 16:40:17', NULL),
(9200, 'AntGame.io', 'antgame-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 15, 781, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/ant-game-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'AntGame.io is an ant simulator puzzle game. Help the ants by placing home tiles in positions that get them the most food. Get more food to score more points and climb the leaderboards in challenge mode. Or sandbox mode is also available if you just want to play with the ants.', 'Left-mouse button to place a tile on the map and click the play button.', 'antgame-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:17', '2022-08-08 16:40:17', NULL),
(9201, 'Tyran.io', 'tyran-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 674, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tyran-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tyran.io is a .io battle royale game with an ability to hatch and ride dinosaurs!\n', '\nWASD to move\nE to interact\nR to reload\nEsc to open the Options menu\nLeft mouse button attack\nRight mouse button to drop items\n', 'tyran-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:18', '2022-08-08 16:40:18', NULL),
(9202, 'MudWars.io', 'mudwars-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 312, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mudwarsio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Hadik.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'MudWars is a fantastic .io game in which you control a tank and must battle other opponents in a field full of mud! Before you start, you can choose your username, tank skin, and server region. When entering the battle you must travel around the map and shoot at the gold nuggets scattered on the ground – destroying a nugget gives you XP and allows you to level your tank up.\n', '', 'mudwars-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:19', '2022-08-08 16:40:19', NULL),
(9203, 'Astroe.io', 'astroe-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 472, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/astroeio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Daniel Phillips.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Get ready for a serious space war in Astroe.io, a new .io game. In the game you control a spaceship and play as a team, either green or red. Your main objective is to capture all satellites; in order to do so, just move your spaceship within the satellite\'s range. Get gold by destroying asteroids or other player\'s spaceships. You can also get passive gold based on the number of captured satellites. Upgrade your spaceship to increase its battle capabilities and satellites to arm them with defensive weapons. Good luck!\n', '', 'astroe-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:19', '2022-08-08 16:40:19', NULL),
(9204, 'Wormania.io', 'wormania-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 891, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/wormania-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'one of the other players – if you crash into their tail then you will be destroyed and have to start', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wormania.io is a cool and intense multiplayer grow game. You must control a neon worm and move around the map – as you move you must collect different colored dots. These dots help your worm grow to an enormous size! Around the map, you can also find a myriad of power-ups that give your worm different abilities.\n', '', 'wormania-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:20', '2022-08-08 16:40:20', NULL),
(9205, 'Bunk.Town', 'bunk-town', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 860, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bunk-town/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bunk.Town is a .io survival game to stay alive and sneak into the infamous Bunkfort Bunker!\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nLeft mouse button to attack/use items\nSpace bar to dash\nQ/E/mouse scroll to switch items\nB to buy items\n', 'bunk-town.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:21', '2022-08-08 16:40:21', NULL),
(9206, 'Bump.io', 'bump-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 144, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bump-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'BPTop.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'There are 16 cars are involved in the competition. You must avoid collisions with the boundaries to win. Bumping other cars give energy, and destroying other cars to give volume growth.\n', '', 'bump-io0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:22', '2022-08-08 16:40:22', NULL),
(9207, 'Stickman Warriors', 'stickman-warriors', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 20, 440, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stickman-warriors/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Viktor Sadovski.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stickman Warriors is an awesome stickman fighting .io game in which you must fight against other players online using your very own deadly stickman warrior. Before you enter the arena you can customise the appearance of your warrior and give them different outfits. Once you have kitted out your stickman warrior you can enter the fray and start fighting!\n', 'Use the WASD keys or the arrow keys to move and attack.', 'stickman-warriorss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:23', '2022-08-08 16:40:23', NULL),
(9208, 'Curve Fever Pro', 'curve-fever-pro', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 13, 630, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/curve-fever-pro/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'trapping them with your curve. Try to avoid smashing into other players\' curves while using your pow', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Curve Fever Pro is an epic multiplayer io game in which you must compete against up to 6 other players around the world. This game contains more features than the original game including a variety of powers you can use to steal points from your opponents. You can customize your in-game avatar as well as your curve with fun skins. ', 'Check out the video trailer on Youtube.', 'curve-fever-pro.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:23', '2022-08-08 16:40:23', NULL),
(9209, 'Mageclash.io', 'mageclash-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 11, 74, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mageclash-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Mattzap.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mageclash.io is a multiplayer fantasy game where you battle monsters and other players in order to become the most powerful player on the server. Battle boss monsters, build your character from hundreds of spells, weapons, and equipment, and become the best fighter! Mageclash.io features a unique customization system where you can combine spells, weapons, armor, and stat allocations to create exactly the character you want. ', '\nWASD or arrow keys = move\n1-4 = change spells\nShift = sprint\nMouse = aim\nF = pick-up\nLeft-click = shoot\n', 'mageclash-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:24', '2022-08-08 16:40:24', NULL),
(9210, 'Towerz.io', 'towerz-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 17, 137, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/towerz-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Murat Yucel.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Towerz.io is a multiplayer blocks-stacking game. Try to stack the blocks as high as you can and with the competition!\n', '', 'towerz-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:24', '2022-08-08 16:40:24', NULL),
(9211, 'gatdamn.io', 'gatdamn-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 1188, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/gatdamn-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'lilshake.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gatdamn.io is an io-multiplayer game to fight and rise to the top of the leaderboard. Join the world and start the battle with each other. Once a player is taken down, you can take and equip your enemy gun and also revive some health from it, so always try to get them before the others. You can also play a private game with your friends.', '\nA / left arrow key = move left\nD / right arrow key = move right\nW / up arrow key / space = jump\n1-9 = switch weapons\nMouse movement = aim\nLeft-click = shoot\nRight-click = zoom out\n', 'gatdamn-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:25', '2022-08-08 16:40:25', NULL),
(9212, 'Hand Spinner IO 3D', 'hand-spinner-io-3d', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 18, 564, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hand-spinner-io-3d/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hand Spinner IO 3D is a superb game about the fidget spinner! You must control a single fidget spinner and try to eliminate other players by knocking out their spinner from the ring.\n', '', 'hand-spinner-io-3d0.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:26', '2022-08-08 16:40:26', NULL),
(9213, 'Senpa.io', 'senpa-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 18, 138, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/senpa-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Azzimi, one of the developers from the hugely popular Agar.io.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Senpa.io is a fantastic multiplayer game that takes inspiration from the hugely successful Agar.io. The gameplay is quite similar – you must move around the arena and try to become the biggest cell!\n', '\nMove your mouse to control the movement\nW to shoot masses\nSpace bar to split\n', 'senpa-io2.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:27', '2022-08-08 16:40:27', NULL),
(9214, 'BattleBoats.io', 'battleboats-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 70, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/battleboatsio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Electronauts, a games studio from Germany. It\'s currently in Beta, so you can expect frequent update', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Battleboats.io is an intense sea battle game in which you compete against other players from around the world. The goal is to destroy your enemies\' base! You need to move the big bomb to the enemy\'s headquarters by picking up the mine crates; the bomb moves closer with each crate you pick up. You can level up your boat by collecting enough experience crates. At certain levels, your boat is upgraded with a better cannon. Shoot down big cannons and other players on the map. You have limited ammo but you can always restock by picking up the ammo crates. Don\'t let the enemies get in your way to glory!', '', 'battleboats-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:28', '2022-08-08 16:40:28', NULL),
(9216, 'Mages', 'mages', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 726, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mages/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'redka.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Mages is a superb 3D multiplayer arena game. In this awesome game, you must take control of a mage and fire loads of cool spells at your opponent. There are several rounds in each game, and the winner is the one with the most round victories.\n', '\nMovement is with WSAD keys \nSkills are Q, E, R, F, Space bar, and Shift\nCasting is with the left mouse click\n', 'mages1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:29', '2022-08-08 16:40:29', NULL),
(9217, 'Drednot.io (Dredark)', 'drednot-io-dredark', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 1038, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/drednot-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Adam Coggeshall.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Drednot.io is a fun battleship style game in which you must develop your own dreadnought ship and crew and sail the seas to battle with other players. You can actually join forces with others too, to create a mighty vessel.\n', '\nWASD to move or climb a ladder\nSpace bar to jump or exit a ladder\nLeft-click to interact\nRight-click to use an item\nQ to drop an item\nMouse scroll to zoom\nC to fast zoom\nEnter to chat\nTab to show the scoreboard\n', 'drednot-io-dredark7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:30', '2022-08-08 16:40:30', NULL),
(9218, 'Bladers', 'bladers', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 733, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bladers-io-bpk/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Ricreator.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bladers.io is one of our interesting fidget spinner games. Grow and power up your gear to the max! Destroy other opponents.\n', '\nHold left mouse button to move\nQ to power up\nW to speed up\n', 'bladers.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:31', '2022-08-08 16:40:31', NULL),
(9219, 'Gulch.io', 'gulch-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 664, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/gulch-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Dygn.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gulch.io is a fun 2D battle royale game. Tactics play an important role in this game as you start with nothing, and you need to find equipment to make yourself stronger. Use the map to be aware of your surroundings and become the winner of the match!\n', '\nWASD to move\nLMB to shoot\nRMB to aim\nF to open a door\nF to pick-up an item\nI to access inventory\nM to open map\nEnter to chat\n', 'gulch-io9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:32', '2022-08-08 16:40:32', NULL),
(9220, 'Narwhale.io', 'narwhale-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 827, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/narwhaleio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Hsi-Hung Shih.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In Narwhale.io you swim around the screen and attack other players by stabbing them. How many of them can you kill before you are killed yourself?\n', '', 'narwhale-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:32', '2022-08-08 16:40:32', NULL),
(9221, 'Generals.io', 'generals-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 16, 313, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/generalsio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Generals.io is a highly tactical strategy game from the ever popular .io games series. In Generals.io you take command of a General square. From there, you must move from square to square, recruiting armies and gaining in numbers and strength; moving about the map until you find, capture and control the opposing general’s tile.', '', 'generals-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:33', '2022-08-08 16:40:33', NULL),
(9222, 'Oib.io', 'oib-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 20, 472, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/oibio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'LapaMauve, the same developer as Limax.io.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oib.io is a .io game in which you have to create your own army of oibs to go to battle. Before playing the game, you can decide which main character\'s class you would like to use; each has its own advantage and disadvantage. In the game, start by spawning several oibs and feed them to your main character. Repeat this until you are big enough, then it\'s time to hunt! You can use your oibs to create your own mass army or join them separately to create new stronger units; send them to other players instead of risking your main character. Remember that the life of spawned units decreases over time. That means that you need to feed them with oibs to restore their health. Have fun conquering the map!', '', 'oib-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:34', '2022-08-08 16:40:34', NULL),
(9224, 'Bomby.io', 'bomby-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 17, 358, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bombyio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Petroglyph Games.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Bomby.io is a fun .io avoid game in which you must move around the map and avoid other players and bombs that litter the playing field. You control a small yellow emoji icon that grows larger as you collect the green gems found on the map. You can also drop bombs that explode after a certain amount of time to try and destroy your opponents.\n', '\nUse your mouse to move\nLeft click to drop a bomb\nRight click to boost speed\n', 'bomby-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:35', '2022-08-08 16:40:35', NULL),
(9225, 'SuperCTF', 'superctf', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 353, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/superctf/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Marshall Demirjian.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'SuperCTF is an interesting team-based ranked multiplayer capture the flag game with several power-ups and weapons.', 'The game is played with a keyboard and mouse but still works fine on a laptop with a touchpad. ', 'superctf.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:36', '2022-08-08 16:40:36', NULL),
(9226, 'Snowballs.io', 'snowballs-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 1183, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/snowballs/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Snowballs.io is a snowball fighting game. Throw the snowballs to the opponents and try your best to climb in the leaderboard!\n', '\nUse the WASD keys or the arrow keys to move\nUse the mouse to aim\nUse the left mouse button to throw a snowball\n', 'snowballs-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:37', '2022-08-08 16:40:37', NULL),
(9227, 'Aquar.io', 'aquar-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 337, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/aquar-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'S3 Games, the same developer who made Oceanar.io and Sworm.io.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aquar.io is an amazing war game set in the deep-sea. It is the sequel to the popular Oceanar.io. In this game, you control an angler fish queen, and you must try to eat many scattered food as possible to spawn different fishes and grow your army.', '\nLeft click to attack\nRight click to merge, hold to devour\nMouse scroll to zoom\n', 'aquar-io9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:38', '2022-08-08 16:40:38', NULL),
(9228, 'Glor.io', 'glor-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 402, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/glorio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Take on the role of a mercenary and survive in the wildlands of Glor.io, a real-time multiplayer .io game. Start by gathering enough food, either by hunting animals or picking up eggs. Then, hire other mercenaries to assist you in gathering resources and fighting other players. After that, you can start to gather wood and stones to build your own base. Build towers to generate gold over time, but make sure to protect them! Your rank is determined by the amount of gold you have. You can also create a clan by sending an invitation to your friends. Have fun!', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\n1 to 9 keys to quickly select building\nLeft click to gather resources and attack\n', 'glor-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:38', '2022-08-08 16:40:38', NULL),
(9229, 'ShootEm.io', 'shootem-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 1129, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/shootemio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ShootEm.io is a fun and exciting multiplayer shooter game in which you must move around a 2D pixelated city and try to eliminate your opponents. Use the WASD or arrow keys to move your character and use your mouse and left click mouse button to aim and fire your weapon. Start with a simple pistol to dish out damage - you can find other weapons hidden around the city and in crates.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nLeft click to shoot\nRight click to enter wall build mode, click again to build the wall\nShift to sprint or drift\nSpace bar to pick up item or enter car\n', 'shootem-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:39', '2022-08-08 16:40:39', NULL),
(11767, 'Drunken Archers Duel', 'drunken-archers-duel', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 437, '0', 'https://www.y8.com/embed/drunken_archers_duel', 'https://y8.com', 'en', 'Y8 Studio', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Drunken Archers Duel a fun and exciting physics game to play. Control the drunken ragdolls, which are holding the bow and arrows to kill each other. As they are acting like a drunk, try to aim your arrow at your opponent and kill them before they kill you. Calculate the correct angle before releasing the arrow from your bow. Challenge your friends to beat you, select any modes between single-player and dual player and win among them. Play a lot more bow and arrow games only on y8.com', '', 'drunken-archers-duell.gif', 1, 1, '2022-08-21 11:09:21', '2022-08-21 11:09:21', NULL),
(9231, 'MudField.io', 'mudfield-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 408, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/mudfield-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'MudField.io was', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'MudField.io is an ultimate warfare game in which two countries have are an all-out war with one another. You can select the country that you wish to fight for and join the fight as one of four different class options. You can select the soldier that best suits your play style and drive earth moving machines such as tanks and military vehicles. ', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nE or shift to enter a vehicle\nG to throw a grenade\nLeft mouse button to shoot\nRight mouse button to use the sniper scope\n123 to switch weapons\n', 'mudfield-iob.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:41', '2022-08-08 16:40:41', NULL),
(9232, 'Sugar Shock (.io)', 'sugar-shock-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 536, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/sugar-shock/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sugar Shock is a competitive match-3 game. You need to match sweets and score as many points as possible within 1 minute. It is made by Jason Kapalka, designer of the original Bejeweled!\n', '', 'sugar-shock-io6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:42', '2022-08-08 16:40:42', NULL),
(9233, 'Endless League', 'endless-league', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 74, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/endless-league/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'killing other players or collecting experience orbs. The first player reaching 10.000 score wins the', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Select your spaceship, customize it however you like and jump into the battlefield. Endless League is a MOBA-like game in which you control your spaceship and have to destroy your opponents.\n', '\nWASD for movement\nHold left mouse button for the 1st skill\nHold right mouse button for the 2nd skill\nMouse scroll to zoom in/out\nE for 3rd skill\nR for ultimate\n', 'endless-leaguee.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:43', '2022-08-08 16:40:43', NULL),
(9234, 'SpaceBlast.io', 'spaceblast-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 19, 951, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/spaceblastio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Ercan G.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This entertaining multiplayer game allows you to control your very own spaceship! Before you start you can choose your spaceships color. Play against 5 other opponents and attempt to destroy them whilst improving your own ships stats. Shot the asteroids in your path to level up your ship and unlock stat points. These points can be used to increase your ships power including its speed and fire rate.\n', '', 'spaceblast-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:43', '2022-08-08 16:40:43', NULL),
(9235, 'NitroClash.io', 'nitroclash-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 15, 1054, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/nitroclashio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Florent.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nitroclash.io is a fast paced 3-on-3 soccer game – you control a colored ball that acts as your player. Using this ball you must move around the soccer pitch and attempt to score a goal with the ball. You control your ball using the mouse and you can give yourself a speed boost using the left click button. Be wary as this speed boost is limited and the power bar refills over time. Furthermore, the space bar applies breaks to slow you down if you need to quickly change direction.\n', '\nMove your mouse to control the movement\nHold space bar to brake or stand still\nC to view the field\nX to lock camera\n', 'nitroclash-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:44', '2022-08-08 16:40:44', NULL),
