(9239, 'Karnage.io', 'karnage-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 852, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/karnageio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Karnage.io is a great multiplayer .io game. Enter the arena and battle other players. Collect weapons, ammo, and armor as you become stronger and stronger. Don\'t fall off the platform, because the lava will kill you! The game features multiple weapons such as the assault rifle, sniper rifle, minigun, pistol, shotgun, and revolver.', '', 'karnage-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:47', '2022-08-08 16:40:47', NULL),
(9240, 'Strike.is', 'strike-is', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 20, 781, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/strikeis/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Strike.is is not your ordinary cell eating game; it\'s a unique multiplayer game in which the goal is to eliminate other cells using various weapons! At first, you are equipped with a crossbow, later you can swap it with other weapons that you will find across the map. Each weapon has unique abilities; use them often to help you in the battle. You can pick up health power-ups to restore lost health. There are several modes available and you can play either solo or as a team. Have fun!', '', 'strike-iss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:40:48', '2022-08-08 16:40:48', NULL),
