(9261, 'Hexar.io', 'hexar-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 124, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hexario/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hexar.io is a great .io game in which you control a colored circle and need to capture as many hexagon blocks as possible. Its gameplay is similar to that of Paper.io, another amazing casual multiplayer game. To capture blocks, connect your trail from non-owned blocks to your owned ones. Be careful when leaving a trail because if an enemy hits you, it is a game over. Start building up your domain little by little to help your maneuver. When you see other players leaving too far away from their area, take your chance to hit them! Avoid hitting the opponent\'s head because you can get killed. Collect green circles to boost your speed. Have fun!', 'You move automatically, left click on the desired area to change direction.', 'hexar-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:03', '2022-08-08 16:41:03', NULL),
(9262, 'Tactics Core', 'tactics-core', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 297, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/stbaio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Christopher Scott, who recently also developed a great multiplayer RTS game, Strike Tactics.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tactics Core is a .io game with a twist – this game allows you to engage in high-tech multiplayer warfare against hundreds of other players online. Before you start fighting, you can choose from a range of different warships such as a roller, a javelin, a silencer, and a manta – each unit has different statistics and weaponry. The graphics are reminiscent of the original Command and Conquer games and the gameplay is similar too.\n', '\nWASD to move\nLeft click to shoot\n1 to use special skill\n', 'tactics-coreo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:04', '2022-08-08 16:41:04', NULL),
(9263, 'Takemine.io', 'takemine-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 89, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/takemineio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Ali al Haulani.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Takemine.io is another fun survival game in which you must move around a 2D world and collect resources to help your survival. You start with an axe and you must use this to chop down trees to gather wood - you can then use this wood to build structures and other tools and weapons.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nArrow keys to switch item\nLeft click or space bar to gather or attack\nE to toggle auto attack\n', 'takemine-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:05', '2022-08-08 16:41:05', NULL),
(9264, 'Braains.io', 'braains-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 14, 892, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/braains-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Jaeyun Noh (m0dE).', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Which side will you choose in Braains.io? Braains.io is an awesome multiplayer game of survival – you start as a human but you can transform into a zombie immediately if you wish and try to turn the other players into a zombie too. ', 'Use the WASD keys or the arrow keys to move the character.', 'braains-io1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:06', '2022-08-08 16:41:06', NULL),
(9265, 'Knifez.io', 'knifez-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 868, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/knifez-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'JointSoft.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Knifez.io is the competitive battle royal game in which you are a cartoon character with a deadly sharp throwing knife. Fight a number of other online players in knife throwing warfare to see who the best knife thrower across the land is. Defeat plenty of opponents and you will be rewarded with an extra life.\n', '', 'knifez-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:07', '2022-08-08 16:41:07', NULL),
(9266, 'Too Many Cooks', 'too-many-cooks', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 383, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/too-many-cooks/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'taking food from the fridge. Once you have mastered the basics you can start upgrading your characte', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Too Many Cooks game - become a Masterchef! Too Many Cooks lets you become a professional cooker with a mission to earn a profit by serving customers. You can only bake pizza at the beginning, but as soon as you earn more profit and level up, you can access more food.', '\nWASD to move\nLeft mouse button to interact\n', 'too-many-cookss.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:08', '2022-08-08 16:41:08', NULL),
(9267, 'Galaxystrife', 'galaxystrife', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 750, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/galaxystrife/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Daniel Vyskoc', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Galaxystrife is a superb multiplayer shooter game based in space! The galaxy has been torn apart by war and you must control a giant spacecraft and vie for power against other players.', '', 'galaxystrife3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:09', '2022-08-08 16:41:09', NULL),
(9268, 'CrowdCity.io (Zombie)', 'crowdcity-io-zombie', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 77, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/crowd-city-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'CrowdCity.io is a unique multiplayer game in which you actually become a zombie! Your goal is simple – to kill and eat as many humans as possible, as well as other zombies too – your hunger knows no limits!\n', '', 'crowdcity-io-zombie1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:09', '2022-08-08 16:41:09', NULL),
(9269, 'Tanx', 'tanx', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 430, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tanx/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tanx is a multiplayer team-based tank battle game. Drive around your tank and shoot other players while collecting upgrades. That is, in one sentence, what Tanx is about. The first team who manages to score enough kills of the enemy tanks wins the game. Discover it for yourself in this great multiplayer arena game!\n', '', 'tanx9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:10', '2022-08-08 16:41:10', NULL),
(9270, 'Limax.io', 'limax-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 19, 788, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/limaxio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Limax.io is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Limax.io is similar to Slither.io, but instead of growing longer and longer, you grow fatter and fatter. Kill others and eat them to grow into the fattest snake ever!', 'Move your mouse to control the snake\'s movement direction. Use the left mouse button or space to accelerate.', 'limax-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:11', '2022-08-08 16:41:11', NULL),
(9271, 'Dogar', 'dogar', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 310, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/dogar/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'OMG so many memes! Dogar is a version of Agar.io with memes everywhere and they are obviously after you... Have fun.', '', 'dogarr.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:12', '2022-08-08 16:41:12', NULL),
(9272, 'Modd.io', 'modd-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 1111, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/moddio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Modd.io is a game portal in which you can access several different versions of a zombie apocalypse. Each game version has a different theme such as Christmas, Halloween and Two Houses. When you have chosen a version you enter the game as a single character and must help defend your immediate area against the zombie threat.\n', '\nTo move, press WASD or arrow keys\nTo grab, press left mouse button\nTo pick up item, press right mouse button\nTo drop item, press G\n', 'modd-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:12', '2022-08-08 16:41:12', NULL),
(9273, 'Tetrio', 'tetrio', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 204, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tetrio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'SPIRITEQ.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tetrio is a Tetris-style game with a goal to push the opponent out of the field.\n', '\nLeft or right arrow to move the tetriminoes\nUp arrow to rotate\nDown arrow to put to the next level\nSpace bar to do a hard drop\n', 'tetrio8.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:13', '2022-08-08 16:41:13', NULL),
(9274, 'Lordz2.io', 'lordz2-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 709, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/lordz2-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Spinbot Studio', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Lordz2.io is a multiplayer .io game made by Spinbot Studio and set in the Middle Ages. In this game, you have to conquer land and expand your territory. Build your castle and key buildings to support your army, then summon various units to help you in your conquest. Strategy plays an important role; make sure every soldier counts!', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move\nSpace bar to dash\nHold left mouse button to attack\nE or right click to activate the special power\nB to build\nU to buy a soldier\nF to arrange army formation\nY to upgrade soldier\nSpace bar to split an army\nC to change formation\nM to toggle minimap\nL to toggle leaderboard\nEnter to chat\nEsc to enter the pause menu\n', 'lordz2-io7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:15', '2022-08-08 16:41:15', NULL),
(9275, 'Flags Quiz', 'flags-quiz', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 216, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/flags-quiz/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Flags Quiz is a fun general knowledge game that tests your knowledge of flags around the world. There are several different game modes in which you can test your flag knowledge. The quiz mode, for example, provides you with flags that you have to spell the country name in a Hangman-style gameplay.\n', '', 'flags-quizz.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:16', '2022-08-08 16:41:16', NULL),
(9276, 'Sea Ride (.io)', 'sea-ride-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 712, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/sea-ride/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sea Ride is a .io game about sea creatures battle for dominance. Become the biggest fish in the sea. Swim in the sea, complete quests, collect powerups and weapons, and eat other fish. But beware, there is always a bigger fish!\n', '', 'sea-ride-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:16', '2022-08-08 16:41:16', NULL),
(9277, 'Uchu.io', 'uchu-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 11, 672, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/uchu-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Uchu.io is a multiplayer spaceship arena game in which you can design, upgrade, and build your ultimate battleship. You start off with a small ship but can add several components to it such as thrusters, reactors, missile turrets, and ion cannons. You can mine asteroids in order to gain resources needed to upgrade your ship and you fight other players in order to level up your ship and become stronger. The game has an FFA game mode in which you can instantly buy stronger ships using minerals you have gained and features faster-paced gameplay. It also has a coop game mode where you get to custom design your own ship and PVP is optional to accept.\n', '\nWASD to move around\nMouse scroll to zoom in/out\n', 'uchu-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:17', '2022-08-08 16:41:17', NULL),
(9278, 'Tetrads.io', 'tetrads-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 18, 132, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tetrads-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Tetrads.io is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tetrads.io is a top-down Tetris-style combat game in which you protect your core body by collecting block pieces. Not only can you use these block pieces to defend yourself, you can also collect them and shape constructions to attack your enemies. By destroying their core bodies, they will randomly drop blocks that you can pick up. Your goal is to become the largest and most powerful floating Tetrads fortress of them all.', '\nMove with mouse\nSpeed boost with left click\n', 'tetrads-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:18', '2022-08-08 16:41:18', NULL);
