(9280, 'Oceanar.io', 'oceanar-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 11, 905, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/oceanario/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oceanar.io - conquer the deep seas! Oceanar.io is a very challenging and highly addicting game from the .io games series. ', '\nLeft mouse button or W to attack\nRight mouse button or space bar to merge\n', 'oceanar-io6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:18', '2022-08-08 16:41:18', NULL),
(9281, 'Paceman.io', 'paceman-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 311, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/pacemanio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Paceman.io is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Paceman.io is a Pacman inspired .io game. You can eat glowing points to make you move faster. To eat other players, you must hit them from behind. Otherwise you will bounce. Eat power-ups that are scattered around the map to get an extra boost, but be careful: not everything has a positive effect. Avoid hitting round saws at any cost; they will kill you. Collect as many points as possible and dominate the leaderboard!', 'Move your mouse to adjust the moving direction. Hold the left mouse button for a brief period and release it to dash.', 'paceman-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:19', '2022-08-08 16:41:19', NULL),
(9282, 'Kazap.io', 'kazap-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 129, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kazapio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kazap.io lets you experience an intense multiplayer starship battle! At first, you control a small starship, but you grow in size. The bigger your size, the bigger your damage. Hunt other players by shooting them with your laser and collecting their orbs when they\'re destroyed. Be careful with the laser fences that border the map, if you touch them, your starship is destroyed. Are you up for a space battle?\n', '', 'kazap-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:20', '2022-08-08 16:41:20', NULL),
(9283, 'Zapper.io', 'zapper-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 15, 875, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/zapper-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Rens Rongen, the maker of Ninja.io.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zapper.io is a fun multiplayer snake-style game in an electric world with unique mechanisms.\n', '\nMove your mouse to control the movement\'s direction\nPress left mouse button to boost speed\n', 'zapper-io7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:21', '2022-08-08 16:41:21', NULL),
(9284, 'Brutal.io', 'brutal-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 15, 537, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/brutalio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Brutal.io is', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Brutal.io is a fantastic multiplayer .io game in which you must control a vehicle that has a circular flair attached. You must try and increase the size of your flail and use it to destroy other players. The size of your flail starts off really small and it grows when you collect the crystals that are scattered on the map – crystals also appear when an enemy is destroyed and the larger they were, the larger the crystals that are dropped.', '\nUse your mouse to move\nLeft click to detach flail\nHold left click to attach flail\n', 'brutal-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:21', '2022-08-08 16:41:21', NULL),
(9285, 'Worms.lol', 'worms-lol', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 1036, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/worms-lol/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Worms.lol is a .io game to become the largest worm and dominate the arena.\n', '', 'worms-lol3.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:22', '2022-08-08 16:41:22', NULL),
(9286, 'Battlefields.io', 'battlefields-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 19, 770, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/battlefields-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Battlefields.io is a strategy game about capturing opponents\' towers. Can you dominate the battlefield?\n', '', 'battlefields-io7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:23', '2022-08-08 16:41:23', NULL),
(9287, 'Warscrap.io', 'warscrap-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 13, 769, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/warscrapio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Evil Noob, LLC.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Warscrap.io is an intense third-person shooting and defense game! Defend the machines against enemy invasions together with your fellow fighters. You get a warning when an enemy is attacking one of your machines. You can buy new guns and characters with the energy that you receive during battle. Good luck!\n', '\nWASD to move\nL to lock/unlock mouse\nSpace bar to jump\nRight click to switch weapon\nLeft click to attack\nE to open shop menu\n', 'warscrap-iob.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:23', '2022-08-08 16:41:23', NULL),
(9288, 'Supercar Stadium', 'supercar-stadium', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 715, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/supercar-stadium/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Supercar Stadium was', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Supercar Stadium is a multiplayer car soccer game with a top-down view!', '\nArrow keys or WASD = move\nHold X or shift = boost\nHold Z or Y = drift\nKeys are customizable\n', 'supercar-stadium9.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:24', '2022-08-08 16:41:24', NULL),
(9289, 'Soccer.io', 'soccer-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 330, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/soccer-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Soccer.io is a cool multiplayer soccer game in which you must complete in a four way battle against three other opponents. You must try and eliminate players from your game by scoring goals against them.\n', '', 'soccer-io1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:25', '2022-08-08 16:41:25', NULL),
(9290, 'Richup.io', 'richup-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 470, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/monno-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Richup is a web-based board game inspired by Monopoly in which you purchase properties and build your financial empire against other players. In the game, all players start with the same amount of cash ($1500). Each player rolls the dice to move forward. Once one landed on a property, it can be purchased, and other players that will land on this property will have to pay its owner. Once you own all properties in a group, you can start upgrading them by building houses and hotels. The more houses or hotels you have in a property, the more players will pay you once they land on it. Your goal is to own as many properties as you can and become the last remaining player.\n', '', 'richup-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:26', '2022-08-08 16:41:26', NULL),
(9291, 'Hexanaut.io', 'hexanaut-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 12, 859, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/hexanaut-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Exodragon Games', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hexanaut.io is an io game to conquer the area as big as you can. Be careful not to cut your own line and also not be cut by another player too. There are totems on the map that can be captured and provide additional bonuses. How big area that you can conquer? Prove your skill in this territory-capturing game.', 'Move the mouse to navigate your character.', 'hexanaut-io6.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:26', '2022-08-08 16:41:26', NULL),
(9292, 'Nightpoint.io', 'nightpoint-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 10, 507, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/nightpointio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Nightpoint.io is a frantic multiplayer shooter in which you must fight in a 2D cityscape against hordes of undead zombies. The graphics are reminiscent of Pokemon games and you can choose from several different 2D characters. To start with you are equipped with a pistol but as you level up you can choose different weapons including a machine gun, a shotgun, and a flame thrower.\n', '\nWASD to move\nLeft click to shoot\n', 'nightpoint-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:27', '2022-08-08 16:41:27', NULL),
(9293, 'CleanUp.IO', 'cleanup-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 10, 994, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/cleanup-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'CleanUp.IO was', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Just like Hole.io, this game allows you to grow bigger and eventually clean the entire map! Start by vacuuming small objects and make your way to victory.', 'Drag the left mouse button to control the vacuum\'s movement.', 'cleanup-io4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:27', '2022-08-08 16:41:27', NULL),
(9294, 'Kirka.io', 'kirka-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 16, 886, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/kirka-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kirka.io is a multiplayer FPS game in the voxel world. Choose your loadout and participate in the Champions League to become the best player!', '\nWASD = move\nSpace = jump\nLeft-click = shoot\nRight-click = aim\nShift = crouch\nE = dash\n1, 2, 3 = switch weapons\n', 'kirka-io4.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:28', '2022-08-08 16:41:28', NULL),
(9295, 'llam.io', 'llam-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 17, 760, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/llam-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Pixel Voices.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'llam.io is a game about the llama. You control a llama and need to stomp other llamas\' head.\n', '\nMove your mouse to control the llama\'s movement\nPress left mouse button to jump\nPress right mouse button to stomp\n', 'llam-io7.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:30', '2022-08-08 16:41:30', NULL),
(9296, 'Trapz.io', 'trapz-io', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 14, 280, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/trapzio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'climbing the platforms and avoiding the traps', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Trapz.io is a fun and intense multiplayer io game in which you must attempt to slay other players whilst avoiding the various dangerous obstacles and traps on the map. This game is based on the popular Trap Adventure 2 platform game and uses much of the same graphics, music and gameplay elements. You control a character who has an immense sword – you must use this sword to destroy everyone around you!\n', '\nAD to move\nW or space bar to jump\nLeft click to attack\n', 'trapz-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:31', '2022-08-08 16:41:31', NULL),
(9297, 'Zorelit.io', 'zorelit-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 10, 87, '0', 'http://games.crazygames.com/en_US/zorelitio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zorelit.io is a cool multiplayer spaceship battle game in which you must try and dominate the galaxy with your kitted out space craft. You can equip your spacecraft with a myriad of different weapons such as missiles, lasers and torpedoes. To control your spaceship you use the mouse and the left click button to fire its weapons. You can even chat to other players using a series of cool emoticons.\n', '\nMove your mouse to control the spaceship\nLeft click or Q to fire\nRight click or W to use an ability\nHold space to lock a direction\n1234 to use an emoticon\n', 'zorelit-iob.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:31', '2022-08-08 16:41:31', NULL),
(9298, 'TankRoyale.io', 'tankroyale-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 14, 359, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/tankroyale-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'TankRoyale.io is an arena multiplayer tank battle game.\n', '\nWASD or arrow keys to drive\nLeft mouse button to shoot\nRight mouse button to use ultimate skill\n', 'tankroyale-io.jpg', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:32', '2022-08-08 16:41:32', NULL),
(9299, 'In Mexico Royale', 'in-mexico-royale', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 12, 797, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/in-mexico-royale/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'JeFawk.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'In Mexico Royale is an interesting battle-royale-themed game about maintaining food and money need.\n', '\nPress space bar to jump\nPress right mouse button to sprint\nPress left mouse button to interact\n', 'in-mexico-royale5.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:33', '2022-08-08 16:41:33', NULL),
(9300, 'Slime.LOL', 'slime-lol', 'HTML5', 0, 3, 18, 1106, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/slime-lol/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Slime.Lol is a multiplayer casual sports game in which you control a slime that you can customize.\n', '\nWASD to move\nSpace bar to jump\nShift to use power shot\n1-4 to use emoticon\n', 'slime-lol8.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:34', '2022-08-08 16:41:34', NULL),
(9301, 'CaptureFlag.io', 'captureflag-io', 'HTML5', 0, 5, 13, 617, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/captureflagio/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'CaptureFlag.io', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Capture the Flag is one of the oldest multiplayer game modes and one that everyone knows. CaptureFlag.io concentrates on this cool game mode in the frantic and fun io world. You must move your character using the WASD through the map. You will encounter obstacles and moving objects that can hinder your progress.', '\nWASD or arrow keys to move around\nSpace bar to give a temporary speed boost\nEnter to chat\n', 'captureflag-ioo.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:35', '2022-08-08 16:41:35', NULL),
(9302, 'c4arena', 'c4arena', 'HTML5', 1, 5, 1000, 917, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/c4arena/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', 'Daniel Vyskoc.', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'c4arena is a fantastic two-player connect-four game. You play against your friend using split controls and you must be the first to create a link of four! You play as either red or yellow color. The gameplay is turn-based – you place a tile, then your friend places one until someone wins the round.\n', '', 'c4arenaa.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:36', '2022-08-19 11:37:30', NULL),
(9303, 'Areena.io', 'areena-io', 'HTML5', 0, 4, 12, 1205, '0', 'https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/areena-io/index.html', 'https://crazygames.com', 'en', '', 34, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Areena.io is a multiplayer adventure game in which you must take on a range of challenging quests. It has RPG elements and you can purchase different weapons and armor to help you succeed.\n', '\nWASD to move\nE to interact\nSpace bar or left mouse button to attack\n', 'areena-io1.png', 1, 1, '2022-08-08 16:41:36', '2022-08-19 11:10:03', '2022-08-19 11:10:03'),
